werful%20Chips%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EApple%20Inc.%20announced%20new%20a%20iMac%2C%20laptops%20and%20the%20third%20generation%20of%20its%20in-house%20Mac%20processor%20line%20on%20Monday%2C%20rolling%20out%20an%20M3%20chip%20with%20major%20improvements%20to%20overall%20performance%20and%20graphics%20horsepower.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20chip%20lineup%20relies%20on%20advanced%203-nanometer%20manufacturing%20technology%20and%20more%20efficiently%20handles%20graphics%20processing%2C%20Apple%20said%20in%20a%20presentation%20Monday.%20The%20base%20model%20has%20eight%20main%20cores%20-%20the%20processing%20engines%20on%20a%20chip%20-%20in%20addition%20to%2010%20cores%20for%20graphics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20was%20part%20of%20a%20%26quot%3BScary%20Fast%26quot%3B-branded%20product%20unveiling%2C%20an%20unusually%20timed%20event%20that%20kicked%20off%20at%205%20p.m.%20California%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENew%20MacBook%20Pro%20models%2C%20also%20unveiled%20at%20the%20event%2C%20will%20run%20the%20new%20processors.%20That%20will%20make%20them%20more%20powerful%20while%20retaining%20their%2022%20hours%20of%20battery%20life%2C%20Apple%20said.%20Apple%20also%20debuted%20a%20version%20of%20its%2024-inch%20all-in-one%20iMac%20that%20runs%20the%20M3.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20homegrown%20semiconductor%20business%20-%20known%20as%20Apple%20Silicon%20-%20has%20become%20a%20prized%20asset.%20Since%20switching%20to%20its%20own%20chips%20from%20Intel%20Corp.%20components%20in%202020%2C%20Apple%20has%20seen%20sales%20of%20its%20Mac%20computers%20grow%20sharply%2C%20helped%20by%20a%20broader%20run-up%20in%20tech%20spending%20during%20the%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20recent%20quarters%2C%20revenue%20began%20to%20slide%20again%20and%20competition%20has%20intensified.%20The%20M3%20launch%20is%20meant%20to%20help%20restore%20Apple's%20advantage%20in%20the%20industry%20and%20get%20the%20Mac%20business%20back%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%