ul%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20with%20any%20secret%20relationship%2C%20the%20stuff%20going%20on%20behind%20closed%20doors%20between%20FTX%20and%20Alameda%20Research%20was%20hard%20to%20explain%20and%20probably%20inappropriate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Sam%20Bankman-Fried%20testifies%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%20in%20his%20criminal%20case%2C%20he%20has%20struggled%20to%20get%20past%20a%20core%2C%20key%20contradiction%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20his%20legal%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-sbf-fraud-trial-ftx-explainer-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20prosecutors%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20violated%20a%20slew%20of%20criminal%20fraud%20and%20money-laundering%20laws%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20stealing%20money%20from%20customers%20on%20FTX%2C%20the%20cryptocurrency%20exchange%20he%20ran%20that%20was%20once%20valued%20at%20%2432%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20allege%20he%20siphoned%20the%20money%20to%20Alameda%20Research%2C%20his%20cryptocurrency%20hedge%20fund%2C%20spent%20it%20on%20flashy%20advertising%2C%20and%20used%20it%20to%20make%20loans%20to%20himself%20and%20other%20executives%20for%20personal%20investments.%20The%20hole%20in%20customer%20funds%20became%20clear%20in%20November%202022%2C%20when%20customers%20tried%20to%20withdraw%20their%20funds%20en%20masse%20and%20FTX%20lacked%20the%20cash%20to%20fulfill%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20took%20the%20unusual%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-trial-will-sbf-testify-witness-defense-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eand%20extremely%20risky%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20step%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-testifies-regrets-not-risk-management-team-ftx-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etestifying%20in%20his%20own%20defense%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20told%20a%20different%20story%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20vas