esieged%20Hamas-run%20Palestinian%20territory%20in%20response%20to%20the%20October%207%20attacks%20--%20the%20deadliest%20in%20Israel's%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20intensifying%20military%20operations%20have%20sharply%20heightened%20fears%20for%20the%202.4%20million%20inhabitants%20of%20Gaza%2C%20where%20the%20Hamas-controlled%20health%20ministry%20says%20more%20than%208%2C300%20have%20been%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20briefing%20to%20foreign%20press%2C%20Netanyahu%20said%20a%20ceasefire%20would%20amount%20to%20surrendering%20to%20Hamas%2C%20whose%20gunmen%20killed%201%2C400%20people%20and%20took%20more%20than%20230%20hostages%2C%20according%20to%20the%20latest%20Israeli%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCalls%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20are%20calls%20for%20Israel%20to%20surrender%20to%20Hamas%2C%20to%20surrender%20to%20terrorism...%20this%20will%20not%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20vowing%20Israel%20would%20%26quot%3Bfight%20until%20this%20battle%20is%20won%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20ally%20the%20United%20States%20also%20objected%20to%20a%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20not%20believe%20that%20a%20ceasefire%20is%20the%20right%20answer%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3Bpauses%26quot%3B%20to%20get%20aid%20into%20Gaza%20should%20be%20considered%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20Israeli%20forces%20battled%20Hamas%20militants%20inside%20the%20narrow%20Palestinian%20territory%20and%20sent%20tanks%20to%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%20concern%20has%20surged%20about%20the%20widening%20humanitarian%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKirby%20said%20Washington%20was%20%26quot%3Bconfident%26quot%3B%20of%20increasing%20the%20number%20of%20aid%20trucks%20to%20Gaza%20through%20the%20Rafah%20crossing%20with%20Egypt%20to%20around%20100%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELimited%20aid%20has%20entered%20Gaza%20from%20Egypt%20under%20a%20US-brokered%20deal%2C%20but%20its%20volume%20has%20fallen%20far%20short%20of%20the%20hundreds%20of%20trucks%20a%20day%20aid%20agencies%20say%20are%20needed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPhilippe%20Lazzarini%2C%20head%20of%20the%20UN%20agency%20for%20Palestinian%20refugees%20UNRWA%2C%20called%20for%20the%20Security%20Council%20to%20demand%20an%20immediate%20humanitarian%20ceasefire.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20system%20in%20place%20to%20allow%20aid%20into%20Gaza%20is%20geared%20to%20fail%20unless%20there%20is%20political%20will%20to%20make%20the%20flow%20of%20supplies%20meaningful%2C%20matching%20the%20unprecedented%20humanitarian%20needs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20Israeli%20tanks%20on%20Gaza%20highway%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Hamas%20attack%20set%20off%20the%20bloodiest-ever%20Gaza%20war%2C%20marked%20by%20weeks%20of%20withering%20aerial%20bombardment%20and%20three%20continuous%20nights%20of%20ground%20operations%20centred%20on%20northern%20Gaza%2C%20which%20Israel%20has%20told%20civilians%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EColumns%20of%20Israeli%20tanks%20and%20armoured%20bulldozers%20were%20seen%20churning%20through%20the%20sand%2C%20and%20snipers%20took%20positions%20inside%20emptied%20residential%20buildings%2C%20in%20footage%20released%20by%20the%20army.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20tanks%20advanced%20for%20more%20than%20an%20hour%20into%20the%20southern%20fringes%20of%20Gaza%20City%20and%20blocked%20the%20main%20north-south%20highway%2C%20%26quot%3Bfiring%20at%20any%20vehicle%20that%20tries%20to%20go%20along%20it%26quot%3B%2C%20an%20eyewitness%20told%20AFP%20by%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAir%20strikes%20also%20cratered%20the%20road%20and%20brought%20down%20buildings%2C%20residents%20said%2C%20before%20the%20tanks%20withdrew.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20ground%20forces%20were%20supported%20by%20heavy%20fire%20from%20the%20air%20and%20artillery%2C%20with%20the%20army%20striking%20more%20than%20600%20targets%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20up%20from%20450%20reported%20by%20the%20military%20a%20day%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20said%20it%20had%20fired%20anti-tank%20missiles%20at%20two%20Israeli%20armoured%20vehicles%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bblows%20delivered%20by%20the%20resistance%20have%20prevented%26quot%3B%20Israeli%20troops%20from%20establishing%20a%20presence%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Israeli%20military%20also%20said%20a%20woman%20soldier%20was%20rescued%20from%20captivity%20after%20an%20operation%20in%20the%20Hamas-run%20territory.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20of%20Ori%20Megidish%20was%20%26quot%3Bsecured%20during%20a%20ground%20operation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20army%20said%2C%20adding%20she%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bmedically%20checked%26quot%3B%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20well%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20said%20the%20international%20community%20must%20demand%20the%20captives%20remaining%20in%20Gaza%20%26quot%3Bbe%20freed%20immediately%2C%20unconditionally%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHamas%20released%20a%20video%20of%20what%20it%20said%20were%20three%20women%20hostages%2C%20seated%20against%20a%20tile%20wall%2C%20although%20the%20time%20and%20place%20of%20the%20recording%20could%20not%20be%20verified.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20called%20in%20an%20agitated%20tone%20for%20Netanyahu%20to%20agree%20to%20Hamas'%20proposed%20exchange%20of%20the%20hostages%20for%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20by%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENetanyahu%20in%20a%20statement%20decried%20the%20clip%20as%20%26quot%3Bcruel%20psychological%20propaganda%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E-%20'Bombing%20followed%20us'%20-%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20more%20than%20230%20hostages%20--%20aged%20between%20a%20few%20months%20and%20above%2080%20--%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20held%20in%20a%20network%20of%20underground%20tunnels%20where%20Hamas%20has%20hid%20its%20military%20infrastructure%20from%20Israeli%20surveillance%20and%20air%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIsrael%20confirmed%20the%20death%20of%20one%20of%20those%20missing%20--%20German-Israeli%20Shani%20Louk%2C%2023%2C%20who%20was%20captured%20by%20Hamas%20when%20its%20gunmen%20stormed%20a%20desert%20music%20festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFear%20and%20desperation%20have%20spiralled%20in%20Gaza%2C%20under%20weeks%20of%20siege%20that%20have%20cut%20off%20water%2C%20food%2C%20fuel%20and%20other%20essentials.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInternet%20access%20was%20severed%20on%20Friday%20but%20restored%20Sunday%20following%20US%20pressure%2C%20State%20Department%20spokesman%20Matthew%20Miller%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20made%20clear%20to%20the%20government%20of%20Israel%20over%20the%20weekend%20that%20communications%20networks%20needed%20to%20be%20restored%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20about%20ensuring%20that%20vital%20information%20flows%2C%20humanitarian%20coordination%20continues%2C%20and%20families%20can%20stay%20in%20touch.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20Nations%20reported%20Sunday%20that%20%26quot%3Bthousands%20of%20people%26quot%3B%20had%20ransacked%20aid%20warehouses%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDonkey%20carts%20were%20lining%20up%20to%20load%20water%2C%20as%20safe%20drinking%20water%20has%20become%20scarce%2C%20in%20Khan%20Yunis%20in%20southern%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20UN%2C%20all%2010%20hospitals%20in%20northern%20Gaza%20have%20received%20evacuation%20orders%20--%20despite%20sheltering%20thousands%20of%20patients%20and%20about%20117%2C000%20displaced%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20displaced%20from%20our%20homes%20to%20the%20hospital%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaza%20City%20resident%20Ashraf%20al-Muzani%2C%2038%2C%20said%20from%20Al-Quds%20hospital%20where%20he%20and%20his%20family%20have%20sheltered%20for%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20bombing%20followed%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20haven't%20been%20able%20t