e-secure-and-trustworthy-artificial-intelligence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20touches%20on%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20possible%20uses%20of%20AI%20and%20generative%20AI%20that%20already%20are%2C%20or%20could%20in%20the%20future%2C%20directly%20impact%20people's%20lives.%20Like%20when%20AI%20technology%20is%20used%20in%20corporate%20decision-making%20related%20to%20housing%2C%20hiring%2C%20or%20even%20jail%20time.%20It%20also%20demands%20a%20new%20level%20of%20transparency%20from%20companies%20engaging%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-layoffs-responsible-ai-team-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecreation%20and%20development%20of%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-regulation-2023-us-eu-china-100-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elarge%20language%20models%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20related%20AI%20tools%20released%20in%20the%20last%20year%20by%20Meta%2C%20Google%2C%20Microsoft%2C%20OpenAI%2C%20and%20others%2C%20are%20not%20subject%20to%20safety%20testing%20outlined%20in%20the%20executive%20order.%20The%20size%20threshold%20is%20so%20high%20that%20currently%20most%20available%20models%20do%20not%20meet%20the%20criteria%20for%20further%20transparency%20called%20for%20in%20Biden's%20executive%20order.%20Although%20all%20of%20the%20major%20tech%20companies%20earlier%20this%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FEnsuring-Safe-Secure-and-Trustworthy-AI.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eagreed%20to%20adhere%20to%20standards%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20responsibility%20and%20training%20in%20their%20AI%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20companies%20that%20do%20meet%20the%20threshold%2C%20they%20will%20need%20to%20notify%20the%20federal%20government%20of%20their%20work%20and%20share%20safety%20testing%20results%20before%20release%20to%20the%20public.%20The%20National%20Institute%20of%20Standards%20and%20Technology%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20set%20%26quot%3Brigorous%20standards%26quot%3B%20for%20such%20testing%2C%20including%20testing%20for%20the%20possibility%20of%20generative%20AI%20tools%20to%20direct%20users%20in%20the%20weaponization%20of%20biological%20weapons.%20Meta's%20Llama%202%20model%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-senate-ai-forum-llama-2-gives-anthrax-instructions-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ealready%20capable%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20telling%20a%20user%20how%20to%20weaponize%20anthrax%2C%20as%20Insider%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20tech%20has%20had%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20head%20start%2C%20but%20I%20think%20we%20moved%20very%20quickly%20to%20catch%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Ben%20Buchanan%2C%20who%20has%20worked%20at%20the%20Biden%20White%20House%20since%202021%2C%20most%20recently%20as%20a%20special%20advisor%20on%20AI%2C%20told%20Insider%20in%20an%208-minute%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20Insider's%20complete%20interview%20with%20Buchanan%2C%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity%2C%20see%20below%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20often%20did%20you%20speak%20to%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20big%20tech%20companies%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20this%20executive%20order%3F%20I%20heard%2C%20for%20instance%2C%20that%20the%20White%20House%20spoke%20to%20Andrew%20Bosworth%20of%20Meta%20pretty%20frequently%2C%20a%20couple%20of%20times%20a%20month.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20senior-level%20conversations%20with%20all%20of%20the%20companies%2C%20but%20not%20really%20about%20the%20EO.%20We%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20company%20conversations%20about%20the%20voluntary%20commitments%20that%20we%20rolled%20out%20in%20July.%20I%20don't%20think%20anyone%20has%20spoken%20to%20Andrew%20Bosworth%20in%20particular%20since%20July%20when%20we%20rolled%20out%20the%20voluntary%20commitments.%20But%20we%20did%20engage%20at%20that%20level%20and%20the%20CEO%20level%20in%20the%20run-up.%20We%20have%20spoken%20to%20the%20companies%20some%20since%20then%2C%20but%20more%20about%20the%20voluntary%20commitments%20than%20about%20the%20EO.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20there%20anything%20about%20the%20voluntary%20commitments%2C%20as%20you%20worked%20on%20them%2C%20that%20was%20a%20sticking%20point%20for%20the%20companies%2C%20that%20you%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20pushback%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20pretty%20collaborative%20relationship%20and%20we%20had%20pretty%20high%20standards%20for%20that.%20The%20companies%20acknowledged%20it%20and%20they%20know%20they%20need%20to%20develop%20safe%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20trustworthy%20products.%20I%20think%20we%20got%20to%20a%20good%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWithin%20the%20order%2C%20it%20says%20that%20companies%20developing%20any%20foundation%20model%20that%20poses%20a%20serious%20risk%20to%20national%20security%20will%20need%20to%20be%20more%20transparent%20and%20disclose%20their%20safety%20testing%2C%20et%20cetera.%20Does%20that%20cover%20most%20anyone%20developing%20an%20LLM%2C%20or%20is%20there%20a%20certain%20size%20or%20threshold%20that%20somebody%20needs%20to%20meet%20to%20be%20required%20to%20do%20that%20disclosure%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20a%20threshold%20and%20we%20tried%20to%20make%20the%20fact%20sheet%20a%20little%20more%20plain%20English%2C%20but%20you'll%20see%20in%20the%20executive%20order%20itself%20when%20the%20text%20comes%20out%2C%20that%20the%20threshold%20applies%20to%20models%20that%20use%20more%20than%2010%20to%20the%2026th%20FLOPs%20in%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20threshold%20is%20adjustable%20by%20the%20Department%20of%20Commerce.%20Technology%20is%20moving%20very%20fast%20in%20this%20space%2C%20but%20that's%20the%20baseline%20threshold.%20And%20then%20there's%20a%20lower%20threshold%20if%20it's%20a%20model%20trained%20primarily%20on%20biological%20sequence%20data%20because%20of%20the%20enhanced%20risk%20in%20that%20space.%20It's%2010%20to%20the%2023rd%20for%20bio%2C%20but%20generally%20speaking%2C%20it's%2010%20to%20the%2026th.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThat's%20big%2C%20huge%20really.%20What%20happens%20when%20somebody%2C%20hypothetically%2C%20gives%20you%20training%20data%20that%20is%20flagged%20by%20a%20federal%20agency%3F%20What's%20the%20process%20then%3F%20Does%20everything%20just%20stop%20and%20the%20company%20is%20in%20trouble%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20that's%20still%20in%20development.%20To%20the%20departments%2C%20we're%20laying%20that%20out%20in%20the%20EO%20the%20direction%20of%20travel%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20can%20imagine%20that%20there's%20some%20kind%20of%20legal%20authority%20that%20would%20come%20into%20play%2C%20depending%20on%20what%20the%20flag%20is.%20Just%20hypothetically%2C%20if%20there%20were%20a%20nuclear%20risk%20in%20play%20from%20a%20system%2C%20you%20would%20implicate%20the%20Atomic%20Energy%20Act%20and%20the%20like.%20So%20this%20is%20about%20getting%20the%20right%20information%20and%20then%20bringing%20the%20appropriate%20authorities%20to%20bear.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20could%20imagine%20a%20world%20in%20which%20Congress%20passes%20legislation%20that%20builds%20on%20what%20we're%20doing%20here%20and%20sets%20up%20a%20licensing%20regime.%20And%20a%20lot%20of%20members%20of%20Congress%20have%20talked%20about%20that.%20We're%20not%20taking%20a%20position%20on%20that.%20But%20what%20we're%20doing%20here%20is%20setting%20a%20direction%20of%20travel%20for%20the%20US%20government%2C%20which%20needs%20to%20know%20that%20these%20systems%20are%20safe%2C%20secure%2C%20and%20trustworthy%20before%20they're%20rolled%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20lot%20of%20the%20order%20is%20a%20directive%20for%20these%20various%20agencies%20to%20act.%20How%20long%20do%20they%20have%20to%20set%20these%20standards%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20Defense%20Production%20Act%20regulations%20that%20force%20the%20disclosure%2C%20that's%2090%20days.%20The%20companies%20are%20doing%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20red%20team%20testing%20already.%20The%20development%20of%20standards%20could%20be%20a%20little%20bit%20longer%20than%20that%2C%20but%20there's%20some%20provisional%20guidance%20on%20standards%20in%20the%20EO%20itself%20that%20largely%20mirrors%20what%20we%20agreed%20to%20in%20the%20voluntary%20commitments%2C%20saying%20these%20are%20the%20kinds%20of%20things%20you%20have%20to%20red-team%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20transparency%20that's%20being%20asked%20for%2C%20is%20it%20just%20the%20future%20models%20or%20is%20it%20current%20models%20that%20have%20already%20been%20rolled%20out%3F%20Does%20it%20apply%20retroactively%20in%20any%20way%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20voluntary%20commitments%20apply%20to%20future%20models.%20It's%20hard%20to%20do%20as%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%20hard%20to%20do%20pre-release%20red%20team%20testing%20for%20a%20model%20that's%20out%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20think%20AI%20is%20in%20a%20hype%20cycle%2C%20and%20everybody's%20overreacting%20to%20what%20it's%20going%20to%20mean%3F%20Given%20how%20many%20models%20are%20out%20there%2C%20how%20powerful%20they%20already%20are%2C%20et%20cetera%2C%20are%20government%20regulators%20everywhere%20a%20little%20bit%20behind%20the%20tech%20right%20now%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20won't%20comment%20on%20hype%20in%20terms%20of%20what%20you%20should%20invest%20in%2C%20but%20I%20think%20from%20a%20government%20perspective%2C%20we%20think%20there%20are%20real%20opportunities%20here%20and%20we%20think%20there%20are%20real%20risks.%20We%20wouldn't%20be%20doing%20this%20accelerated%20comprehensive%20action%20if%20we%20thought%20this%20was%20all%20going%20to%20fade%20away%20in%20a%20week.%20This%20is%20a%20priority%20for%20the%20President%20and%20his%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20terms%20of%20being%20behind%20the%20tech.%20The%20tech%20has%20had%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20head%20start%2C%20but%20I%20think%20we%20moved%20very%20quickly%20to%20catch%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20thing%20I%20point%20to%20is%20we%20secured%20agreement%20from%20the%20G7%20on%20the%20first-ever%20international%20code%20of%20conduct%20on%20AI%2C%20which%20builds%20upon%20the%20voluntary%20commitments%20that%20have%20been%20signed%20off%20on%20by%20all%20seven%20governments%20in%20the%20G7.%20The%20United%20States%20is%20working%20in%20conjunction%20with%20allies%20and%20partners%20and%20is%20moving%20very%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDo%20you%20use%20generative%20AI%2C%20Ben%3F%20Does%20anybody%20in%20your%20office%20use%20it%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EB.B.%3A%20To%20my%20knowledge%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20ChatGPT%20on%20the%20systems%20here%2C%20but%20all%20of%20us%20use%20AI%20every%20single%20day%20as%20we%20go%20about%20daily%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%20or%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20Kali%20Hays%20at%20khays%40insider.com%2C%20on%20the%20secure%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20949-280-0267%2C%20or%20through%20DM%20on%20X%20at%20%40hayskali.%20Reach%20out%20using%20a%20nonwork%20device.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-advisor-catching-up-on-ai-biden-executive-order-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698700472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6525496d55f52b01b35ab94d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhite-house-advisor-catching-up-on-ai-biden-executive-order-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Biden%20on%20Monday%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20on%20AI%20technology%20that%20calls%20for%20more%20transparency%20and%20rules.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Kali%20Hays)%22%2