Cp%3EFor%20the%20first%20seven%20months%20of%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20presidency%2C%20the%20chief%20executive%20coasted%20in%20national%20approval%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMonth%20after%20month%2C%20an%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprojects.fivethirtyeight.com%2Fbiden-approval-rating%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaverage%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20his%20national%20approval%20ratings%20stayed%20double%20digits%20above%20his%20disapproval%20ratings.%20That%20is%2C%20until%20the%20US%20began%20its%20process%20of%20completely%20withdrawing%20its%20military%20forces%20from%20Afghanistan%2C%20coinciding%20with%20Biden's%20approval%20ratings%20consistently%20declining%20in%20that%20same%20period%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Taliban%20seized%20control%20of%20Afghanistan's%20capital%2C%20Kabul%2C%20in%20mid-August%20of%202021%20and%2013%20US%20soldiers%20were%20killed%20assisting%20with%20the%20withdrawal%20on%20August%2026%2C%202021%2C%20Biden's%20disapproval%20ratings%20finally%20overtook%20his%20approval%20ratings%2C%20a%20trend%20he's%20yet%20to%20be%20able%20to%20flip%2C%20namely%20due%20to%20a%20near-twenty-percentage-point%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gallup.com%2Fpoll%2F513305%2Fdemocrats-ratings-biden-slip-overall-approval.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edownswing%20among%20independents.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Biden%20approval%20October%202023%20Gallup%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fe35a96f7540cd069699f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221022%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGallup%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20also%20notably%20appear%20to%20have%20dropped%20their%20support%20for%20Biden%20amidst%20the%20Afghanistan%20withdrawal%20to%20the%20tune%20of%20around%20ten%20percentage%20points%2C%20about%20half%20the%20drop%20of%20the%20independent%20voters.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20new%20war%2C%20however%2C%20has%20emerged%20in%20recent%20weeks%20that%20could%20be%20just%20as%20consequential%20to%20Biden's%20reelection%20chances%20if%20not%20more%20so%20than%20the%20tumultuous%20Afghanistan%20withdrawal%3A%20Israel's%20fight%20against%20Hamas%20following%20the%20group's%20terrorist%20attacks%20against%20civilians%20in%20early%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Biden's%20approval%20ratings%20amongst%20Republicans%20have%20remained%20level%20since%20the%20war%20began%2C%20his%20support%20from%20Democrats%20has%20dropped%20approximately%20ten%20percentage%20points%20in%20recent%20weeks%2C%20from%20around%2085%25%20approval%20to%2075%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20drop%20in%20support%20is%20unlikely%20to%20come%20from%20those%20who%20believe%20Biden%20isn't%20doing%20enough%20to%20support%20the%20Jewish%20state%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%20Biden's%20already%20asked%20Congress%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-gaza-palestine-ukraine-aid-biden-requests-100-billion-congress-2023-10%5C%22%3E%2414.3%20billion%20in%20aid%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20Israel%20and%20personally%20flew%20to%20the%20country%20to%20meet%20with%20Israeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20and%20show%20his%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fd3nkl3psvxxpe9.cloudfront.net%2Fdocuments%2FIsrael-Hamas_War_poll_results.pdf%5C%22%3EYouGov%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20offers%20a%20clue%20as%20to%20why%20Biden's%20approval%20rating%20amongst%20Democrats%20is%20falling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20asking%201%2C000%20US%20citizens%2C%20the%20pollster%20found%20that%20Democrats%20were%20slightly%20more%20likely%20than%20Republicans%20and%20independents%20to%20sympathize%20with%20Palestinians%20in%20the%20war%20than%20Israelis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20also%20found%20that%20Democrats%20said%20they%20sympathized%20%26quot%3Bequally%26quot%3B%20with%20both%20groups%20at%20a%20