ss%20for%20our%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20that%20people%20can't%20invest%20in%20there.%20We%20just%20look%20at%20asset%20classes%20or%2C%20you%20know%2C%20what%20belongs%20in%20a%20long-term%20portfolio%2C%20what%20has%20intrinsic%20value%2C%20has%20cash%20flows%20to%20it%3F%20And%20those%20are%20the%20asset%20classes%20we%20steer%20people%20towards.%20And%20so%20we%20don't%20go%20towards%20bitcoin%20or%20gold%20or%20any%20other%20of%20those%20stable%20assets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesman%20later%20told%20Insider%20that%20Vanguard%20views%20the%20investment%20case%20for%20cryptocurrencies%20as%20weak.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUnlike%20stocks%20and%20bonds%2C%20most%20cryptocurrencies%20lack%20intrinsic%20economic%20value%20and%20generate%20no%20cash%20flows%2C%20such%20as%20interest%20payments%20or%20dividends%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BFurther%2C%20cryptocurrencies%20have%20proven%20to%20be%20highly%20volatile%2C%20which%20runs%20counter%20to%20Vanguard's%20goal%20to%20generate%20positive%20real%20returns%20to%20investors%20over%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20BlackRock's%20spot%20bitcoin%20ETF%20application%20remains%20under%20review%20by%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission.%20While%20the%20regulator%20allows%20bitcoin%20futures%20ETFs%2C%20it%20has%20been%20largely%20critical%20of%20the%20cryptocurrency%20sphere%2C%20and%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fetf%2Fbitcoin-etf-spot-sec-ark-21-shares-crypto-market-2023-9%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%3Epreviously%20denied%20such%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20August%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-grayscale-trust-gbtc-crypto-etf-conversion-sec-lawsuit-2023-8%5C%22%3EGrayscale%20Investments%20won%20its%20court%20case%20against%20the%20SEC%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0which%20had%20ea