05G-powered%20greenhouse%20in%20Japan%20grows%20tomatoes.%3Cp%3ENTT%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%20%3Cli%3EJapan's%20agriculture%20industry%20is%20being%20affected%20by%20an%20aging%20population%20and%20shrinking%20workforce.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EIn%20remote%20locations%2C%205G-powered%20tech%20is%20helping%20farmers%20produce%20crops%20with%20the%20support%20of%20experts.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EPrivate%205G%20is%20better%20for%20agriculture%20because%20it%20can%20cover%20rural%20areas%20more%20reliably.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EThis%20article%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2F5-g-playbook%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-uri%3D%5C%222cfab16c921eca6c291e91a3bdbaf459%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-5g-wireless-technology-shaping-our-world-2023-7%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22summary_bullets%5C%22%3E5G%20Playbook%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20series%20exploring%20one%20of%20our%20time's%20most%20important%20tech%20innovations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EJapan's%20aging%20workforce%20and%20declining%20population%20are%20having%20significant%20effects%20on%20the%20country's%20agriculture%20industry.%20The%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.e-stat.go.jp%2Fen%2Fstat-search%2Ffiles%3Ftclass%3D000001150922%26cycle%3D7%26year%3D20200%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2020%20Census%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Forestry%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20between%202015%20and%202020%2C%20the%20number%20of%20agriculture%20workers%20in%20Japan%20dropped%20by%20over%2020%25.%20Of%20the%20remaining%20farm%20workers%2C%20almost%2070%25%20were%2065%20or%20older.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20effort%20to%20revitalize%20the%20industry%2C%20private%20companies%20and%20local%20governments%20are%20partnering%20to%20develop%20technologies%20that%20can%20take%20some%20of%20the%20pressure%20off%20aging%20farmers%20and%20a%20shrinking%20workforce%2C%20and%20technology%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-frequency-is-5g%5C%22%3E5G%20mobile%20internet%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20playing%20an%20important%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E5G-powered%20technology%20is%20helping%20farmers%20monitor%20crops%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJapanese%20farmers%20are%20essential%20for%20producing%20major%20exports%20such%20as%20rice%2C%20barley%2C%20and%20wheat%2C%20all%20of%20which%20are%20also%20in%20demand%20domestically.%20Smart-farming%20technologies%20can%20help%20make%20farming%20easier%20and%20more%20efficient%20as%20the%20workforce%20changes%2C%20said%20Abe%20Masakuza%2C%20the%20head%20of%20management%20strategy%20and%20implementation%20at%20NTT%20AgriTechnology%2C%20the%20agricultural-production%20division%20of%20Nippon%20Telegraph%20and%20Telephone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221439%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20Abe%20Masakuza%20wearing%20a%20black%20a%20blazer%20in%20front%20of%20plants.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6539646c96f7540cd065b5be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221079%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAbe%20Masakuza%2C%20the%20head%20of%20management%20strategy%20and%20implementation%20at%20NTT%20AgriTechnology.%3Cp%3ENTT%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20approach%20is%20environmentally%20friendly%2C%20eliminates%20travel%20time%2C%20and%20allows%20experts%20to%20support%20more%20farmers%20in%20a%20limited%20amount%20of%20time%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20reduction%20of%20labor%20shortages%20in%20agriculture%20and%20the%20realization%20of%20profitable%20farming%2C%26quot%3B%20Masakuza%20said%20in%20an%20email%20to%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmart%20farming%20was%20introduced%20into%20Japanese%20agriculture%20in%202020%20by%20NTT%20AgriTechnology%20in%20Ch%C5%8Dfu%20City%2C%20Tokyo%2C%20for%20a%20three-year%20project.%20Experts%20from%20the%20local%20government's%20agricultural-research%20center%20in%20Tachikawa%2C%20Tokyo%2C%20about%20an%20hour's%20drive%20away%2C%20provided%20support%20to%20the%20farmers%20in%20Ch%C5%8Dfu%20City%20via%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-5g%5C%22%3E5G-powered%20technology%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20enabling%20farming%20without%20on-the-ground%20assistance.%20The%20experts%20helped%20the%20farmers%20grow%20crops%20with%20fully%20remote%20instruction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20same%20year%2C%20the%20first%205G-powered%20electric%20robotractors%20hit%20the%20ground%20in%20Iwamizawa%2C%20a%20city%20in%20Northern%20Japan.%20The%20machinery%20was%20created%20through%20partnerships%20between%20Hokkaido%20University%2C%20NTT%2C%20and%20local%20governments%2C%20and%20demonstrated%20that%205G%20was%20capable%20of%20reliably%20transmitting%20large%20amounts%20of%20information%20from%20the%20tractors%20to%20data-monitoring%20sites.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobotractors%20and%205G-connected%20robots%20allowed%20farmers%20to%20remotely%20monitor%20crops%20in%20multiple%20fields%20from%20a%20single%20location%20and%20receive%20assistance%20from%20experts%20in%20agricultural%20research.%20Robots%20powered%20by%205G%20also%20helped%20farmers%20remotely%20spray%20pesticides%2C%20cut%20grass%2C%20and%20perform%20other%20physically%20demanding%20tasks%20that%20would%20otherwise%20be%20strenuous%20on%20the%20aging%20workforce.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrucially%2C%205G%20allows%20farmers%20to%20transmit%204K%20footage%20in%20real%20time%20because%20of%20its%20significant%20bandwidth%2C%20Masakuza%20said%2C%20a%20feat%20that%20would%20be%20challenging%20if%20done%20exclusively%20on%20WiFi%20networks.%20This%20helps%20farmers%20monitor%20crops%20for%20disease%20and%20create%20a%20harvesting%20timeline%20while%20navigating%20conditions%20that%20can%20change%20daily.%20Even%20more%20importantly%2C%20the%20low%20latency%20integral%20to%205G%20technologies%20ensures%20that%20experts%20can%20operate%20robots%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ability%20to%20quickly%20stop%20and%20control%20the%20robot%20remotely%20is%20crucial%20from%20a%20safety%20standpoint%2C%26quot%3B%20Masakuza%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20private%205G%20makes%20actual%20robot%20operation%20possible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFarmers%20benefit%20from%20this%20system%2C%20Masakuza%20said%2C%20because%20it%20allows%20them%20to%20receive%20support%20from%20experts%20daily%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20weekly%20or%20even%20monthly%20assistance%20they%20had%20previously.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221579%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20of%20two%20farming%20experts%20looking%20at%20two%20large%20monitors%20displaying%20agricultural%20data.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653bbdc096f7540cd0678749%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221184%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EExperts%20can%20help%20farmers%20with%20limited%20agricultural%20experience%20from%20a%20remote%20office%20called%20%26quot%3Bthe%20cockpit.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3ENTT%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20no%20longer%20have%20to%20check%20on%20their%20crops%20every%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Masakuza%20said.%20%26quot%3BImages%20and%20data%20can%20be%20easily%20collected%20and%20analyzed.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20several%20case-study%20scenarios%2C%205G%20technology%20has%20been%20deployed.%20In%20Ch%C5%8Dfu%20City%2C%20NTT%20built%20fully%20automated%20greenhouses%20where%20farmers%20used%205G-powered%20technology%20such%20as%20smart%20glasses%20to%20control%20variables%20including%20temperature%20and%20humidity.%20In%20the%20case%20study%2C%20the%20greenhouses%20reduced%20the%20burden%20on%20farmers%20and%20protected%20crops%20from%20extreme%20weather.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%205G%20allowed%20Ch%C5%8Dfu%20City%20workers%20without%20an%20agriculture%20background%20to%20receive%20remote%20instruction%20from%20experts%2C%20then%20successfully%20grow%20tomatoes%20and%20funnel%20the%20crops%20back%20into%20the%20local%20food%20supply.%20Ready%205G%20access%20means%20instruction%20can%20occur%20in%20high%20resolution%20and%20in%20real%20time.%20Tomato%20plants%20benefit%20from%20these%20innovations%20because%20in%20the%20Japanese%20climate%2C%20which%20is%20generally%20hot%20and%20humid%2C%20they%20require%20constant%20monitoring%20to%20grow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPrivate%205G%20networks%20are%20proving%20more%20reliable%20for%20innovation%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJapan's%205G%20network%20already%20covers%20about%2055.5%25%20of%20the%20population%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.soumu.go.jp%2Fmain_sosiki%2Fjoho_tsusin%2Feng%2Fpressrelease%2F2022%2F10%2F21_02.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewith%20the%20goal%20being%2095%25%20coverage%20by%20the%20end%20of%202023%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20of%20this%20coverage%20comes%20from%20mobile-phone%20providers%20that%20offer%20public%20networks.%20Smart-farm%20producers%2C%20however%2C%20are%20hoping%20to%20increase%20the%20development%20of%20private%2C%20local%20networks%20that%20bring%20coverage%20to%20rural%20farming%20regions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flas-vegas-private-5g-network-2023-9%5C%22%3EPrivate%205G%20networks%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20better%20for%20agriculture%20because%20they're%20more%20customizable%20to%20meet%20the%20needs%20of%20local%20conditions%20and%20can%20cover%20rural%20areas%20more%20reliably%2C%20Shahid%20Ahmed%2C%20the%20executive%20vice%20president%20of%20new%20ventures%20and%20innovation%20at%20NTT%2C%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20tractors%20have%20become%20really%20advanced%2C%20and%20they%20have%20to%20be%20connected%20all%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20Ahmed%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20we%20move%20toward%20real-time%20analysis%20and%20machine%20learning%2C%20you%20need%20t