0of%20uranium%20has%20risen%20by%20a%20whopping%20125%25%20since%20the%20end%20of%202020%2C%20and%20uranium%20ETF%20assets%20grew%20twenty-fold%20in%20the%20same%20time%2C%20according%20to%20Bloomberg%20Intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sprott%20Uranium%20Miners%20ETF%2C%20which%20holds%20shares%20of%20companies%20involved%20in%20uranium%20production%20and%20also%20holds%20the%20physical%20commodity%2C%20is%20up%2040%25%20this%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENuclear%20power%20plants%20produce%20power%20by%20splitting%20an%20atom%20%E2%80%94%20uranium%20%E2%80%94%20which%20releases%20large%20amounts%20of%20energy%20in%20the%20form%20of%20heat%20and%20radiation.%20Uranium%20is%20the%20most%20commonly%20used%20metal%20in%20nuclear%20plants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20not%2C%20however%2C%20unbridled%20enthusiasm%20across%20all%20uranium%20stocks.%20According%20to%20Bloomberg%2C%20some%20that%20have%20gained%20significant%20value%2C%20like%20Global%20X%20Uranium%20ETF%2C%20which%20has%20rocketed%2030%25%20higher%20this%20year%2C%20are%20now%20being%20shorted%20by%20hedge%20fund%20managers%20who%20are%20also%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20shares%20that%20could%20stumble.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20International%20Energy%20Administration%2C%20an%20estimated%20%2440%20billion%20has%20been%20invested%20into%20nuclear%20power%20every%20year%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years.%20That%20number%20needs%20to%20more%20than%20triple%20to%20reach%20the%20%24125%20billion%20annual%20investment%20required%20to%20meet%20net-zero%20emissions%20by%20the%20middle%20of%20this%20century.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENuclear%20power%20has%20been%20controversial%20among%20non-fossil%20fuel%20sources%20of%20energy%20since%20the%20Fukushima%20accident%20in%20Japan%20in%202011%2C%20when%20an%20earthquake%20caused%20three%20nuclear%20reactors%20to%20overheat%20and%20leak%20toxic%20radioactive%20elements%20into%20the%20environment.%20Thousands%20of%20people%20had%20to%20evacuate%20the%20area%2C%20and%20the%20site%20is%20still%20undergoing%20a%20clean%20up%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20climate%20change%20impels%20governments%20and%20economies%20to%20commit%20to%20net-zero%20goals%2C%20nuclear%20power%20is%20back%20on%20the%20table%E2%80%93which%20means%20uranium%20is%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Furanium-stocks-hedge-funds-nuclear-power-future-commodity-climate-change-2023-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698694262000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653fd26d356802a56be77cde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Furanium-stocks-hedge-funds-nuclear-power-future-commodity-climate-change-2023-10%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bloomberg%20reports%20hedge%20fund%20managers%20are%20expecting%20a%20dramatic%20rise%20in%20the%20price%20of%20uranium%2C%20a%20key%20element%20used%20in%20nuclear%20power.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asoni%40insider.com%20(Aruni%20Soni)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A16%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Furanium-stocks-hedge-funds-nuclear-power-future-commodity-climate-change-2023-10%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Halloween%20weekend%20shootings%20across%20US%20leave%20at%20least%2011%20dead%2C%20scores%20injured%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698694035000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104835037%2Cimgsize-65788.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fhalloween-weekend-shootings-across-us-leave-at-least-11-dead-scores-injured%2Farticleshow%2F104835032.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104835032.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D