Sanon%2C%20filmmaker%20Punit%20Malhotra%2C%20Suniel%20Shetty%20along%20with%20his%20children%20Ahan%20Shetty%20and%20Athiya%20Shetty%2C%20Richa%20Chadha%20and%20Ali%20Fazal%2C%20Aayush%20Sharma%20and%20Arpita%20Khan%20Sharma%2C%20Imran%20Khan%20and%20his%20girlfriend%20Lekha%20Washington%20were%20seen%20arriving%20at%20the%20venue%20to%20celebrate%20Kriti%20Kharbanda's%2033rd%20birthday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fimran-khan-makes-a-rare-appearance-with-girlfriend-lekha-washington-at-kriti-kharbandas-birthday-bash-arpita-khan-suniel-shetty-among-others-also-attend%2Farticleshow%2F104834247.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIndefinite%20Suspension%20A%20Concern%26quot%3B%3A%20Supreme%20Court%20In%20Raghav%20Chadha%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20indefinite%20suspension%20of%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20right%20of%20the%20people%20to%20be%20represented%20while%20calling%20the%20exclusion%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20political%20opposition%20from%20the%20house%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20matter%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20and%20Justices%20JB%20Pardiwala%20and%20Manoj%20Misra%20also%20questioned%20whether%20the%20Privileges%20Committee%20could%20issue%20such%20an%20order%20to%20indefinitely%20suspend%20an%20MP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20remarked%2C%20%26quot%3BSuch%20kind%20of%20indefinite%20suspension%20will%20have%20ramifications%20on%20the%20people%20whose%20constituency%20is%20going%20unrepresented%3F%20Where%20is%20the%20power%20of%20the%20privilege%20committee%20to%20indefinitely%20suspend%20the%20member%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20exclusion%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20political%20opposition%20from%20the%20House%20was%20a%20serious%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apex%20court%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BMember%20should%20have%20verified%20the%20consent%20of%20the%20other%20members%20to%20be%20part%20of%20select%20committee%20but%20is%20this%20a%20breach%20of%20privilege%3F%20Exclusion%20of%20members%20of%20the%20opposition%20from%20the%20House%20is%20a%20serious%20matter.%20He%20is%20representative%20of%20a%20voice%20that%20is%20different%20than%20the%20ruling%20party%20and%20this%20is%20an%20important%20concern%20for%20the%20constitutional%20court.%20Indefinite%20suspension%20is%20a%20cause%20of%20concern%20and%2075%20days%20have%20gone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESenior%20advocate%20Rakesh%20Dwivedi%2C%20appearing%20for%20Chadha%2C%20said%20the%20MP%20respects%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20that%20he%20had%20apologised%20earlier%20too%20and%20was%20now%20doing%20it%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20would%20look%20into%20the%20issue%20of%20indefinite%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPlease%20have%20the%20joint%20compilation%20sent%20to%20us%20by%20Thursday%205%20at%20pm.%20We%20will%20hear%20on%20Friday%20then.%20We%20will%20also%20hear%20on%20the%20extent%20of%20interference%20and%20that%20this%20is%20not%20a%20final%20punishment%20but%20a%20pro%20tem%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%20Raghav%20Chadha%20moved%20the%20top%20court%20challenging%20his%20indefinite%20suspension%20from%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChadha%20was%20suspended%20from%20the%20Upper%20House%20on%20August%2011%20for%20%26quot%3Bbreach%20of%20privilege%26quot%3B%20during%20the%20Monsoon%20Session%20after%20complaints.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20MP%20was%20accused%20of%20not%20obtaining%20the%20consent%20of%20five%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MPs%20before%20including%20their%20name%20in%20a%20select%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20suspended%20till%20the%20Privilege%20Committee%20submitted%20its%20findings%20on%20the%20allegation%20against%20him%20for%20forging%20the%20signatures%20of%20five%20MPs%20in%20a%20motion%20related%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Services%20Bill%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChadha%20has%20called%20the%20suspension%20patently%20illegal%20and%20without%20the%20authority%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20suspension%20followed%20a%20motion%20moved%20by%20Leader%20of%20the%20House%20Piyush%20Goyal%20who%20sought%20action%20against%20the%20AAP%20leader%20for%20including%20names%20of%20some%20members%20of%20the%20Upper%20House%20without%20their%20consent%20in%20a%20proposed%20select%20committee%20for%20the%20Government%20of%20National%20Capital%20Territory%20of%20Delhi%20(Amendment)%20Bill%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698689820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F5g4hlugs_raghav-chadha-ani_625x300_08_August_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findefinite-suspension-a-concern-supreme-court-in-raghav-chadha-case-4528824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%20expressed%20concern%20over%20the%20indefinite%20suspension%20of%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20Raghav%20Chadha%20and%20its%20impact%20on%20the%20right%20of%20the%20people%20to%20be%20represented.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findefinite-suspension-a-concern-supreme-court-in-raghav-chadha-case-4528824%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findefinite-suspension-a-concern-supreme-court-in-raghav-chadha-case-4528824%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2