22title%22%3A%22Delhi%20Liquor%20Policy%20Case%3A%20ED%20Summons%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20for%20Questioning%20on%20November%202%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F19232428%2FScreenshot-2023-05-19-at-11.23.50-PM.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20has%20summoned%20Delhi%20chief%20minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20November%202%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20Delhi%20liquor%20scam.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20has%20been%20summoned%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20to%20record%20his%20statement%20before%20the%20investigation%20agency%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leaders%20%E2%80%93%20Manish%20Sisodia%2C%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20and%20Vijay%20Nair%20%E2%80%93%20are%20already%20in%20prison%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case.%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20name%20has%20been%20mentioned%20in%20the%20case%20charge%20sheet%20multiple%20times%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20accused%20individuals%20had%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20AAP%20chief%20regarding%20the%20formulation%20and%20execution%20of%20a%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy%2C%20which%20was%20rolled%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20connection%20with%20the%20alleged%20scam%2C%20two%20cases%20have%20been%20filed%20by%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20the%20ED%20on%20allegations%20of%20irregularities%20during%20the%20formulation%20and%20implementation%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Excise%20Policy%202021-22.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sisodia%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20ED%20in%20February%20and%20by%20the%20CBI%20in%20March%2C%20Singh%20was%20arrested%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20October.%20ED%20named%20Sisodia%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Ckey%20conspirator%E2%80%9D%20in%20its%20charge%20sheet%2C%20and%20accused%20Singh%20of%20exploiting%20and%20gaining%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20money%2Fkickbacks%2C%20which%20is%20proceeds%20of%20crime%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%20Nair%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20was%20arrested%20in%20September%20last%20year%2C%20after%20being%20accused%20of%20acting%20as%20a%20middleman%20between%20the%20%E2%80%98South%20Group%E2%80%99%2C%20which%20allegedly%20gave%20Rs%20100%20crore%20as%20kickbacks%20to%20enter%20the%20liquor%20retail%20segment%20in%20the%20Capital%2C%20and%20the%20AAP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20related%20development%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Monday%2C%20October%2030%2C%20dismissed%20the%20bail%20plea%20of%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENote%3A%20This%20is%20a%20developing%20story.%20It%20will%20be%20updated%20as%20new%20information%20trickles%20in.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698688378000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F19232428%2FScreenshot-2023-05-19-at-11.23.50-PM.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-case-ed-summons-arvind-kejriwal-for-questioning-on-november-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kejriwal's%20name%20has%20been%20mentioned%20in%20the%20charge%20sheet%20multiple%20times%2C%20stating%20that%20other%20accused%20in%20the%20case%20had%20been%20in%20contact%20with%20him%20regarding%20the%20formulation%20and%20execution%20of%20the%20Delhi%20Liquor%20Policy%202021-22.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdelhi-liquor-policy-case-ed-summons-arvind-kejriwal-for-questioning-on-november-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Many%20Instances%20of%20Academic%20Un-Freedom%20in%20India%20Stem%20From%20Rising%20Hindu%20Nationalism%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F10%2F29155319%2F15980295568_f52b87c70b_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Violence%20and%20academic%20penalties%20against%20student%20expression%20are%20prevalent%20in%20India%20and%20many%20such%20incidents%20seemingly%20stemmed%20from%20an%20authoritarian%20environment%20related%20to%20Hindu%20nationalism%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scholarsatrisk.org%2Fresources%2Ffree-to-think-2023%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20report%20released%20today%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Scholars%20at%20Risk%20(SAR)%20network%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESAR%20is%20an%20international%20organisation%20that%20works%20to%20protect%20scholars%20and%20promote%20academic%20freedom.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEvery%20year%20since%202015%2C%20it%20has%20published%20reports%20on%20trends%20in%20attacks%20on%20academic%20freedom%20around%20the%20world%20titled%20%E2%80%98Free%20to%20Think%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%202023%20edition%20of%20%E2%80%98Free%20to%20Think%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%93%20which%20analysed%20409%20attacks%20on%20higher%20education%20in%2066%20countries%20and%20territories%20between%20July%202022%20and%20June%202023%20%E2%80%93%20found%20that%20such%20attacks%20are%20a%20global%20problem%20and%20occur%20in%20diverse%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndia%20is%20a%20group%20of%2016%20countries%20from%20which%20SAR%20profiled%20concerning%20cases%20in%20more%20detail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20%E2%80%9Cmost%20notable%20violations%20of%20student%20expression%E2%80%9D%20SAR%20noted%20in%20India%20during%20the%20reporting%20period%20was%20the%20action%20taken%20against%20students%20who%20tried%20to%20watch%20the%20BBC%E2%80%99s%20documentary%C2%A0%3Cem%3EIndia%3A%20The%20Modi%20Question%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20documentary%20is%20critical%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20role%20in%20the%202002%20Gujarat%20riots%20as%20chief%20minister%20of%20that%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20called%20the%20documentary%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-india-64634711%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9Chostile%20propaganda%20and%20anti-India%20garbage%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20directed%20YouTube%20and%20Twitter%20to%20take%20down%20links%20leading%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESAR%20noted%20that%20the%20police%20detained%20Delhi%20University%20(DU)%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fjamia-students-detained-bbc-documentary-modi-2002-gujarat%5C%22%3EJamia%20Millia%20Islamia%3C%2Fa%3E%20students%20in%20January%20for%20trying%20to%20publicly%20screen%20the%20documentary.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20noted%20that%20students%20from%20DU%20as%20well%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fdespite-admin-cutting-power-and-alleged-stone-pelting-jnu-students-screen-bbcs-modi-documentary%5C%22%3Eother%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Frajasthan-central-university-bbc-narendra-modi-documentary-abvp%5C%22%3Euniversities%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20punished%20or%20threatened%20for%20planning%20or%20trying%20to%20watch%20the%20-documentary%20%E2%80%93%20in%20one%20case%2C%20DU%20students%20were%20detained%20by%20police%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2FDelhi%2F11-detained-at-protest-against-du-action-over-bbc-film%2Farticle66657873.ece%5C%22%3Efor%20protesting%20the%20suspension%20of%20a%20fellow%20student%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20incident%20from%20DU%E2%80%99s%20track%20record%20that%20made%20it%20to%20SAR%E2%80%99s%20report%20was%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fdelhi-news%2Fdelhis-ip-college-students-protest-harassment-at-fest-11-detained-101680112558414.html%5C%22%3Epolice%20detained%20students%20protesting%20against%20the%20alleged%20harassment%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20their%20classmates%20at%20the%20Indraprastha%20College%20for%20Women%20during%20their%20annual%20fest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F8gYkcqExkac%3Fsi%3D-_EmNRC8IgQ7b4zh%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20also%20tracked%20an%20instance%20of%20action%20against%20university%20teachers%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fsouth-asian-university-suspends-four-faculty-members%5C%22%3Ewhen%20the%20South%20Asian%20University%20suspended%20four%20of%20its%20faculty%3C%2Fa%3E%20members%20for%20supporting%20students%20who%20had%20protested%20against%20reduced%20stipends%20and%20lack%20of%20adequate%20representation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CExpulsions%2C%20dismissals%2C%20suspensions%2C%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20professional%20retaliation%20or%20silencing%20can%20have%20a%20corrosive%20effect%20on%20institutional%20autonomy%2C%E2%80%9D%20SAR%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20continued%20to%20warn%20that%20they%20can%20%E2%80%9Ceven%20contribute%20to%20brain%20drain%2C%20as%20scholars%20and%20students%20seek%20fairer%20and%20more%20transparent%20environments%20in%20which%20to%20conduct%20their%20research%2C%20teaching%2C%20and%20studying.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Education%20as%20a%20space%20to%20promote%20dominant%20ideologies%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESAR%20went%20on%20to%20identify%20instances%20across%20the%20world%20where%20authoritarian%20governments%20were%20encroaching%20on%20academic%20spaces%20to%20fulfil%20their%20agendas.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRising%20global%20illiberalism%20and%20democratic%20backsliding%20means%20that%20governments%20are%20increasingly%20using%20their%20regulatory%20powers%20to%20encroach%20on%20academic%20space%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20some%20of%20the%20most%20closed%20and%20authoritarian%20contexts%2C%20higher%20education%20is%20being%20used%20as%20a%20space%20to%20promote%20specific%20dominant%20ideologies.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20instance%20it%20found%20in%20India%20was%20the%20University%20Guidelines%20Commission%E2%80%99s%20introduction%20of%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timeshighereducation.com%2Fnews%2Fmandatory-indian-knowledge-course-seen-indoctrination%5C%22%3Emandatory%20course%20on%20Indian%20knowledge%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20critics%20said%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20colour%20the%20syllabus%20with%20the%20ruling%20party%E2%80%99s%20ideology.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fy5MywQPi9IY%3Fsi%3DiDNIHK4ufB1HqNFC%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ESimilar%20incidents%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fhistory%2Fncert-history-textbooks-mughals-india%5C%22%3Einvolving%20the%20revision%20of%20syllabi%3C%2Fa%3E%20perceived%20to%20be%20favourable%20to%20the%20ruling%20government%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feducation%2Fremove-our-names-from-textbooks-yogendra-yadav-suhas-palshikar-reiterate-their-demand-to-ncert%5C%22%3Etaken%20place%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20recent%20past.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUniversity%20complicity%20with%20the%20government%20was%20also%20a%20concern%2C%E2%80%9D%20SAR%20continued%20to%20say%2C%20noting%20that%20DU%20and%20Gujarat%20University%20have%20stymied%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fentire-political-science-modi-kejriwal-gujarat-university%5C%22%3Eattempts%20to%20inspect%3C%2Fa%3E%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20degrees.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20of%20Modi%2C%20the%20report%20also%20acknowledges%20that%20two%20DU%20students%20were%20effectively%20confined%20to%20their%20home%20ahead%20of%20a%20university%20event%20featuring%20Modi%20as%20chief%20guest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELocal%20police%20allegedly%20told%20the%20students%20that%20they%20were%20being%20detained%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D%20as%20they%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20create%20%5Ba%5D%20ruckus%20at%20the%20DU%20event%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDU%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdu-colleges-stir-controversy-with-mandatory-attendance-for-valedictory-ceremony%5C%22%3Ewent%20out%20of%20its%20way%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0to%20ensure%20student%20compliance%20during%20the%20ceremony%2C%20with%20some%20of%20its%20colleges%20mandating%20attendance%20at%20screenings%20of%20the%20event%20and%20barring%20students%20from%20wearing%20black-coloured%20clothing%2C%20a%20common%20symbol%20of%20dissent.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EG.N.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20%3Cstrong%3ESaibaba%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESAR%20dedicated%20a%20section%20of%20its%20report%20to%20scholars%20in%20prison%20to%20whom%20it%20said%20it%20provided%20public%20support%20over%20the%20past%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCollectively%2C%20these%20individuals%2C%20imprisoned%20for%20their%20peaceful%20academic%20and%20expressive%20activities%20and%20associations%2C%20are%20subjected%20to%20judicial%20harassment%3B%20unfair%20or%20inadequate%20legal%20proceedings%3B%20lengthy%20pre-trial%20detention%20and%2For%20sentences%3B%20abuse%20and%20torture%20in%20custody%3B%20denial%20of%20access%20to%20legal%20counsel%2C%20appropriate%20medical%20care%2C%20or%20family%3B%20and%20other%20forms%20of%20mistreatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said%20in%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20added%20that%20these%20actions%20also%20affect%20the%20wider%20academic%20community%20by%20sending%20a%20message%20that%20%E2%80%9Cexpressing%20ideas%20or%20raising%20questions%20can%20have%20dire%20consequences%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fremembering-stan-swamy-whose-struggle-was-driven-by-empathy-and-love%5C%22%3ERemembering%20Stan%20Swamy%2C%20Whose%20Struggle%20Was%20Driven%20by%20Empathy%20and%20Love%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20these%20scholars%20is%20G.N.%20Saibaba.%20SAR%20presents%20the%20details%20of%20his%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIts%20report%20quotes%20UN%20special%20rapporteur%20on%20human%20rights%20defenders%20as%20saying%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20%E2%80%9C%5BSaibaba%E2%80%99s%5D%20continued%20detention%20is%20shameful.%20It%20bears%20all%20the%20hallmarks%20of%20a%20State%20seeking%20to%20silence%20a%20critical%20voice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESaibaba%20is%20a%20former%20Delhi%20University%20English%20professor%20who%20had%20travelled%20to%20tribal%20areas%20and%20engaged%20in%20activism%20on%20their%20behalf.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20arrested%20in%202014%20and%20sentenced%20to%20life%20imprisonment%20in%202017%20for%20having%20links%20to%20Maoist%20rebels.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20he%20was%20discharged%20from%20prison%20by%20the%20Bombay%20high%20court%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsc-sets-aside-bombay-hc-order-discharging-g-n-saibaba-in-maoist-links-case%5C%22%3Ethe%20Supreme%20Court%20set%20aside%20the%20discharge%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20April.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20wheelchair-bound%20with%20over%2090%25%20physical%20disability%20and%20has%20alleged%20medical%20negligence%20several%20times%20during%20his%20incarceration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20co-accused%2C%20Pandu%20Pora%20Narote%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fpandu-narote-gn-saibab-convict-dies-swine-flu%5C%22%3Edied%20in%20August%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year%20after%20contracting%20swine%20flu%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESAR%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%20to%20have%20noticed%20the%20decline%20of%20academic%20freedom%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20update%20to%20its%20%E2%80%98Academic%20Freedom%20Index%2C%E2%80%99%20the%20V-Dem%20Institute%20noted%20earlier%20this%20year%20that%20India%20is%20among%2022%20c