0href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flemtinsei-singson-commander-of-manipur-ceasefire-linked-insurgent-group-arrested-with-brown-sugar-by-assam-rifles-4486741%5C%22%3Esigned%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%3C%2Fa%3E%20(SoO)%20agreement%20with%20the%20centre%20and%20the%20state%20government.%20These%20insurgent%20groups%20along%20with%20some%20civil%20society%20organisations%20in%20valley-majority%20Imphal%20have%20come%20under%20intense%20scrutiny%20over%20alleged%20participation%20in%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20has%20killed%20over%20180%20and%20left%20thousands%20internally%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F4pivepag_manipur-violence_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Manipur%20ethnic%20violence%20has%20claimed%20the%20lives%20of%20over%20180%20people%20(File)%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EMs%20Mon%20was%20first%20detained%20by%20the%20Assam%20Rifles%20during%20routine%20checking%20in%20August%20last%20year%20on%20the%20highway%20connecting%20Imphal%20with%20the%20border%20trading%20town%20Moreh.%20The%20Assam%20Rifles%20in%20a%20statement%20had%20said%20they%20found%20an%20expired%20Norwegian%20passport%20and%20an%20Indian%20e-visa%2C%20and%20she%20came%20to%20India%20in%20May%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20took%20her%20into%20custody%20and%20kept%20her%20in%20Imphal's%20central%20jail%2C%20until%20she%20got%20bail%20in%20February%20this%20year%2C%20after%20which%20an%20Imphal-based%20human%20rights%20organisation%20run%20by%20local%20activist%20Babloo%20Loitongbam%20helped%20her%20find%20a%20women's%20shelter%20home%20to%20stay.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20case%20of%20Ms%20Mya%20Kyay%20Mon%2C%20a%20Norwegian%20citizen%20of%20Myanmar%20origin%2C%20was%20brought%20to%20the%20attention%20of%20HRA%20(Human%20Rights%20Alert)%20by%20the%20Myanmar%20language%20instructor%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Myanmar%20Studies%20of%20Manipur%20University...%20HRA%20took%20up%20her%20case%20as%20a%20'woman%20in%20distress%20case'%20and%20informed%20the%20Royal%20Norwegian%20Embassy%20in%20Delhi.%20Thereafter%2C%20she%20was%20issued%20a%20fresh%20Norwegian%20passport%20as%20her%20old%20one%20had%20expired%2C%26quot%3B%20HRA%20executive%20director%20Mr%20Loitongbam%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20in%20response%20to%20local%20media%20reports%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20In%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20ethnic%20unrest%20in%20Manipur%20and%20when%20the%20NGO%20(shelter%20home)%20expressed%20their%20discomfort%20in%20keeping%20her%2C%20we%20organised%20an%20air%20ticket%20for%20her%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20state.%20We%20have%20been%20informed%20she%20was%20summoned%20by%20the%20court%20to%20appear%20in%20her%20pending%20trial%20in%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Loitongbam%20said%20in%20the%20statement%2C%20adding%20they%20did%20not%20know%20Ms%20Mon%20before%20and%20after%20her%20arrest%20in%20August%20last%20year%2C%20until%20the%20moment%20they%20met%20her%20in%20the%20Imphal%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20activist%2C%20who%20is%20also%20a%20fierce%20critic%20of%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N%20Biren%20Singh%20and%20whose%20house%20was%20vandalised%20by%20a%20mob%20earlier%20this%20month%20over%20his%20comments%20on%20two%20Meitei%20organisations%2C%20said%20HRA%20only%20gave%20%26quot%3Blegal%20and%20humanitarian%20services%26quot%3B%20when%20requested%20by%20a%20woman%20in%20distress%20%26quot%3Bas%20per%20our%20mandate%20as%20an%20organisation%20defending%20the%20human%20rights%20for%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20purportedly%20given%20by%20Ms%20Mon%20to%20the%20media%20said%20she%20left%20Manipur%20in%20May%20when%20ethnic%20violence%20broke%20out%20and%20lived%20in%20Delhi%20for%20two%20months.%20She%20then%20went%20to%2