ernment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETata%20Motors%20announced%20on%20Monday%20that%20it%20has%20won%20the%20arbitral%20proceedings%2C%20which%20centred%20on%20the%20loss%20of%20its%20capital%2C%20and%20now%20the%20company%20can%20recover%20Rs%20765.78%20crore%20plus%20interest%20from%20WBIDC.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20not%20a%20final%20verdict%20or%20a%20verdict%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20This%20is%20a%20ruling%20by%20an%20arbitral%20tribunal.%20It%20doesn't%20mean%20this%20is%20the%20end%20of%20the%20road%20for%20the%20state%20government.%20Legal%20avenues%20are%20still%20open%2C%26quot%3B%20TMC%20MP%20Sougata%20Roy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20controversy%20surrounding%20the%20abandoned%20car%20manufacturing%20plant%20in%20Singur%20in%20Bengal's%20Hooghly%20district%20dates%20back%20to%202008%20when%20Tata%20Motors%2C%20facing%20opposition%20led%20by%20TMC%20chief%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20announced%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20its%20ambitious%20Nano%20car%20production%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20the%20CPI(M)-led%20Left%20Front%20was%20in%20power%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20BJP%20accused%20the%20TMC%20of%20driving%20industries%20away%20from%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBJP%20spokesperson%20Samik%20Bhattacharya%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20against%20forcible%20land%20acquisition.%20But%20when%20the%20industry%20started%2C%20we%20wanted%20the%20factory%20to%20come%20up.%20For%20the%20wrong%20policies%20of%20the%20CPI(M)%20and%20the%20militant%20agitation%20of%20the%20TMC%2C%20the%20Tatas%20were%20forced%20out%20of%20the%20state%2C%20permanently%20driving%20industries%20away.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20official%20statement%2C%20Tata%20Motors%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20respect%20of%20arbitration%20proceedings%20between%20Tata%20Motors%20Limited%20and%20WBIDC%2C%20this%20is%20to%20inform%20that%20the%20aforesaid%20pending%20arbitral%20proceedings%20before%20a%20three-member%20Arbitral%20Tribunal%20has%20now%20b