xact%20location.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20unidentified%20woman%2C%20part%20of%20a%2027-member%20marriage%20party%2C%20told%20reporters%20that%20people%20in%20her%20coach%20tumbled%20down%20as%20soon%20the%20brakes%20were%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChildren%20got%20badly%20hurt.%20I%20am%20unable%20to%20walk.%20One%20person%20got%20crushed%20between%20two%20seats%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20sobbing%20woman%2C%20even%20as%20frantic%20rescue%20efforts%20were%20going%20on%20around%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20survivors%20were%20talking%20to%20media%2C%20injured%20persons%20were%20being%20moved%20on%20stretches%20away%20from%20the%20accident%20site%20for%20medical%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20noble%20gesture%2C%20a%20policeman%20carried%20one%20of%20the%20injured%20survivors%20from%20the%20railway%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAnother%20survivor%20from%20Kothavalasa%2C%20who%20was%20asleep%20when%20the%20trains%20collided%2C%20said%20he%20was%20tossed%20to%20the%20floor%20of%20the%20coach%20from%20an%20upper%20berth.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBefore%20I%20could%20realise%20what%20had%20happened%2C%20we%20saw%20our%20coach%20and%20two%20others%20turning%20turtle%20and%20getting%20mangled...people%20were%20lying%20scattered%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20coach.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20boy%20who%20came%20with%20me%20got%20stuck%20in%20a%20seat%20(until%20Sunday%20night%20after%20the%20accident).%20I%20saw%20a%20person%20die.%20There%20were%20so%20many%20people%20in%20the%20coach.%20Children%20got%20injured.%20Some%20suffered%20broken%20limbs.%20We%20found%20an%20opening%20and%20managed%20to%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20even%20as%20his%20white%20shirt%20got%20bloodied%20in%20the%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndica