%20You%20with%20its%20Kindness%20and%20Sincerity%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30212955%2FThe-Wire-62.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EI%E2%80%99ll%20admit%20I%20kept%20my%20distance%20from%20Vidhu%20Vinod%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20thinking%20it%20would%20eventually%20deliver%20the%20same%20old%20spiel%20about%20India%E2%80%99s%20rat%20race%2C%20something%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20assaulted%20with%20in%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%202008%20production%20%3Cem%3E3%20Idiots%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20umpteen%20TVF%20shows%20on%20India%E2%80%99s%20many%20competitive%20entrance%20exams.%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20middling%20work%20as%20a%20director%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades%20post-%3Cem%3EParinda%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20probably%20had%20something%20to%20do%20with%20it%2C%20ensuring%20my%20cynicism%20remained%20despite%20a%20promising%20start.%20I%20was%20almost%20confident%20that%20it%20was%20only%20a%20matter%20of%20time%20before%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20graph%20would%20plummet.%20Hence%2C%20I%20was%20surprised%20to%20find%20myself%20holding%20my%20breath%20during%20the%20final%20stretch.%20It%20was%20around%20then%20that%20I%20realised%20that%20the%20film%20had%20me%20in%20its%20palm%2C%20and%20I%20was%20desperately%20rooting%20for%20the%20protagonist%20%E2%80%93%20Manoj%20Kumar%20Sharma%20(Vikrant%20Massey)%20%E2%80%93%20a%20boy%20out%20of%20a%20village%20in%20Chambal%20(Madhya%20Pradesh)%2C%20preparing%20for%20his%20UPSC%20exams%20in%20Delhi.%20It%20was%20also%20during%20this%20very%20scene%20when%20I%20realised%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20film%20had%20floored%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20painfully%20old%20story%20of%20an%20underdog%2C%20built%20around%20India%E2%80%99s%20unforgiving%20and%20unequal%20education%20system.%20A%20boy%20living%20in%20a%20faraway%20village%2C%20sees%20an%20impossible%20dream.%20The%20first%20time%20we%20see%20him%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20furiously%20making%20notes.%20A%20voiceover%20clarifies%20%E2%80%93%20he%E2%80%99s%20making%20chits%20on%20the%20day%20before%20his%2012th%20board%20exams.%20We%20see%20a%20municipal%20school%20and%20callous%20teachers%20%E2%80%93%20the%20kind%20who%20write%20%E2%80%9Cborad%20exams%E2%80%9D%20on%20the%20blackboard%20without%20a%20second%20thought.%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20goal%20is%20to%20pass%20his%20boards%20so%20he%20can%20take%20up%20the%20job%20of%20an%20office%20peon.%20All%20he%20has%20to%20do%20is%2C%20replicate%20the%20answers%20from%20his%20chits%20into%20the%20answer%20sheet.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FWeMJo701mvQ%3Fsi%3Dpu7jhc2_R9EXuWs9%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%20for%20Manoj%20and%20other%20students%2C%20an%20honest%20cop%20(Priyanshu%20Chatterjee)%20enters%20the%20picture.%20He%20won%E2%80%99t%20allow%20any%20cheating%20during%20boards%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20the%20entire%20batch%20fails.%20It%E2%80%99s%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20the%20likes%20of%20Manoj%2C%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20had%20a%20role%20model%20in%20their%20lives%20until%20then.%20Almost%20starstruck%20by%20the%20cop%20and%20his%20aura%2C%20he%20makes%20up%20his%20mind%20%E2%80%93%20he%20will%20become%20a%20police%20officer%2C%20just%20like%20the%20DSP%20in%20his%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20last%20savings%20of%20his%20grandmother%20(thanks%20to%20her%20monthly%20armed%20forces%20pension)%2C%20Manoj%20makes%20his%20way%20to%20Gwalior%20first%2C%20and%20then%20eventually%20to%20Delhi.%20Training%20his%20eyes%20on%20the%20UPSC%20%E2%80%93%20arguably%20the%20toughest%20exam%20to%20crack%20in%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20life%20becomes%20a%20rollercoaster%20over%20the%20next%207-8%20years%2C%20and%20we%20become%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%E2%80%99s%20barely%20anything%20in%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20we%20haven%E2%80%99t%20seen%20before.%20A%20new%20boy%20in%20a%20strange%20city%2C%20having%20all%20his%20belongings%20stolen%20on%20the%20very%20first%20day%20%E2%80%93%20it%20used%20to%20be%20a%20staple%20scene%20in%20most%20Hindi%20films%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20involved%20the%20characters%20making%20their%20way%20to%20Bombay.%20And%20yet%2C%20it%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20feel%20repetitive%20in%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20film%2C%20because%20we%E2%80%99re%20personally%20invested%20in%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20journey.%20We%E2%80%99re%20in%20his%20shoes%2C%20as%20he%20makes%20the%20decision%20to%20not%20go%20back%20home%20until%20he%E2%80%99s%20made%20something%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%2C%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20work%20like%20it%20does.%20It%E2%80%99s%20not%20the%20most%20novel%20story%2C%20and%20the%20obstacles%20are%20something%20we%E2%80%99re%20all%20acutely%20aware%20of%2C%20even%20possibly%20desensitised%20to.%20A%20boy%20from%20hinterland%20India%2C%20barely%20scraping%20through%20his%2012th%20boards%2C%20living%20in%20a%20big%20city%2C%20someone%20who%20misreads%20%E2%80%98tourism%20in%20India%E2%80%99%20as%20%E2%80%98terrorism%20in%20India%E2%80%99%2C%20someone%20who%20has%20to%20work%2012-15%20hours%20a%20day%20so%20he%20can%20study%20for%20six%20hours%20and%20then%20survive%20on%20three%20hours%20of%20sleep.%20The%20odds%20are%20so%20comprehensively%20stacked%20against%20him%2C%20no%20one%20would%20blame%20him%20for%20failing%2C%20or%20giving%20up.%20But%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20becomes%20%E2%80%9Cinspirational%E2%80%9D%20about%20this%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20journey%20we%E2%80%99ve%20been%20on%20in%20earlier%20films%2C%20but%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20a%20stellar%20%E2%80%98feel%E2%80%99%20for%20authenticity.%20It%20makes%20a%20few%20surprising%20choices%20%E2%80%93%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20lack%20of%20proficiency%20in%20English%20is%20never%20mocked%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20source%20for%20tragedy.%20The%20teacher%20at%20the%20coaching%20centre%20could%E2%80%99ve%20been%20someone%20with%20tics%2C%20which%20could%20be%20mined%20for%20humour.%20Instead%2C%20Chopra%20casts%20Vikas%20Divyakirti%2C%20who%20runs%20a%20coaching%20centre%20for%20UPSC%20exams%20in%20real%20life.%20Unlike%20the%20eccentric%20teachers%20we%E2%80%99ve%20seen%20in%20films%2C%20Divyakirti%20uses%20his%20tranquil%20voice%20to%20bring%20a%20thousand%20racing%20minds%20%5Bin%20his%20class%5D%20to%20a%20pause.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20a%20small%20part%20of%20the%20world%20of%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20but%20it%20helps%20the%20audience%20fully%20immerse%20itself%20in%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20journey.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20surrounds%20his%20protagonist%20with%20a%20lovely%20bunch%20of%20actors%20%E2%80%93%20Anshuman%20Pushkar%20(who%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20Netflix%20show%20%3Cem%3EJamtara%3C%2Fem%3E)%20plays%20the%20%E2%80%98veteran%E2%80%99%20in%20the%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20area%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it.%20So%2C%20he%20makes%20it%20his%20life%E2%80%99s%20mission%20to%20coach%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20hopefuls%2C%20especially%20those%20with%20limited%20means%20like%20Manoj.%20There%E2%80%99s%20Anantvijay%20Joshi%20as%20Pandey%20%E2%80%93%20the%20narrator%20of%20the%20film%20%E2%80%93%20who%20studies%20alongside%20Manoj%2C%20but%20is%20significantly%20more%20%E2%80%98well-settled%E2%80%99.%20Harish%20Khanna%2C%20playing%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20father%2C%20undertakes%20his%20own%20journey%20of%20fighting%20a%20lengthy%20legal%20battle%20against%20his%20superiors%20in%20a%20government%20office%20and%20is%20handed%20the%20film%E2%80%99s%20finest%20scene%2C%20where%20he%20tells%20his%20son%20the%20uselessness%20of%20upright%20honesty%20in%20the%20world.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20voice%20of%20a%20man%20with%20a%20bitter%20awakening%20too%20late%20in%20his%20life%20%E2%80%93%20only%20to%20be%20reminded%2C%20by%20his%20own%20son%2C%20of%20the%20values%20he%20passed%20on%20to%20his%20son.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAbove%20all%2C%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20paean%20to%20Vikrant%20Massey%E2%80%99s%20astronomical%20amounts%20of%20sincerity.%20Manoj%E2%80%99s%20journey%20through%20all%20the%20obstacles%20could%20also%20serve%20as%20a%20parallel%20for%20Massey%20%E2%80%93%20a%20gifted%20young%20actor%20%E2%80%93%20charting%20his%20way%20through%20the%20jungle%20of%20a%20Bollywood%20career.%20Just%20like%20any%20other%20walk%20of%20life%2C%20the%20system%20benefits%20a%20certain%20kind%20of%20prospect%2C%20and%20rarely%20reciprocates%20hard%20work.%20He%E2%80%99s%20never%20been%20terrible%20even%20in%20the%20most%20questionable%20films%20of%20his%20career%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20personal%20victory%20to%20see%20a%20film%20doing%20justice%20to%20Massey%E2%80%99s%20dedication%20to%20throwing%20himself%20into%20a%20part.%20Seeing%20Manoj%20emerge%20from%20the%20darkest%20holes%20and%20greet%20people%20with%20a%20wide%20smile%2C%20despite%20going%20through%20the%20most%20trying%20phases%2C%20is%20an%20image%20from%20the%20film%20that%20I%E2%80%99ll%20carry%20with%20me%20for%20a%20long%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EVidhu%20Vinod%20Chopra%E2%80%99s%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20almost%20feels%20like%20an%20early%20Rajkumar%20Hirani%20film%20%E2%80%93%20when%20simplicity%20of%20thought%20didn%E2%80%99t%20necessarily%20culminate%20into%20contrived%20screenwriting.%20And%20where%20the%20story%20always%20knew%20how%20to%20play%20a%20delicate%20dance%20of%20good%20intentions%20and%20entertainment.%20Unlike%20most%20underdog%20films%20in%20mainstream%20Hindi%20cinema%2C%20where%20one%20eye%20is%20on%20the%20box%20office%2C%20the%20tears%20and%20catharsis%20in%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20always%20feel%20earned.%20This%20could%E2%80%99ve%20very%20easily%20been%20a%20sappy%2C%20sentimental%20film%20%E2%80%93%20but%20Chopra%20never%20compromises%20the%20idealism%20in%20his%20story%20for%20an%20easier%2C%20cheaper%20way.%20%3Cem%3E12th%20Fail%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20proof%20that%20crowd-pleasing%20films%20can%20find%20a%20way%20to%20be%20so%2C%20without%20losing%20sight%20of%20their%20integrity.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698681931000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30212955%2FThe-Wire-62.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fvidhu-vinod-chopras-12th-fail-floors-you-with-its-kindness-and-sincerity%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20could%20have%20been%20another%20humdrum%20film%20about%20the%20underdog%2C%20but%20the%20director%20avoids%20cheap%20and%20easy%20traps.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A38%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ffilm%2Fvidhu-vinod-chopras-12th-fail-floors-you-with-its-kindness-and-sincerity%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Briton%20extradited%20to%20Germany%20and%20charged%20with%20murder%20carried%20out%2044%20years%20ago%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698681780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F10%2F768x432%2Fskynews-munich-istock_6341881.jpg%3F20231030170601%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-70-year-old-extradited-to-germany-over-murder-of-man-found-dead-in-bathtub-in-1979-12996683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Briton%20has%20been%20extradited%20to%20Germany%20and%20charged%20with%20the%20murder%20of%20a%20man%20almost%2045%20years%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fbritish-70-year-old-extradited-to-germany-over-murder-of-man-found-dead-in-bathtub-in-1979-12996683%22%2C%