0into%20an%20annual%20sports%20gathering%20featuring%20four%20events.%20In%20the%20current%20edition%20that%20started%20in%20August%202023%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20the%20girls%20under%20their%20wing%20are%20competing%20right%20from%20the%20village%20level%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20nationals%20organised%20by%20the%20trust.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20organisation%20first%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F318867%2Ffirst-woman-indian-footballer-to-play-english-league-she-kicks-academy-underprivileged-girls-aditi-chauhan%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elooked%20to%20introduce%20sports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20faced%20a%20challenge%20of%20not%20having%20anyone%20on%20the%20staff%20who%20could%20lead%20a%20sports-focused%20initiative.%20Fortunately%2C%20they%20found%20the%20right%20candidate%20in%20Lisa%20Murawsky%2C%20who%20has%20been%20an%20international%20sports%20consultant%2C%20educator%20and%20coach%20for%20over%2020%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERohini%20(now%20the%20Head%20of%20Global%20Partnerships%20and%20Strategy)%20and%20Lisa%20together%20created%20the%20%E2%80%98Sports%20for%20Life%E2%80%99%20programme%20for%20the%20foundation%2C%20which%20led%20to%20the%20birth%20of%20the%20these%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Currently%2C%20the%20Toofaan%20Games%20have%20turned%20into%20an%20annual%20sports%20gathering%20featuring%20four%20events.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_431405561881398_5937455252951809380_n-1698680810.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F260595224_4314055