unravel.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20sources%2C%20Kumar%20was%20accompanied%20by%20Ram%20Bikhari%2C%20another%20worker%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20when%20he%20left%20the%20brick%20kiln%20on%20Monday%20morning%20to%20visit%20the%20bank.%20%E2%80%9CBikhari%20has%20been%20taken%20away%20by%20police%20for%20questioning%20to%20know%20more%20details%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20a%20source%2C%20ruling%20out%20any%20foul%20play%20involving%20Bikhari.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20migrant%20worker%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Unnao%20district%20has%20become%20the%20first%20non-local%20casualty%20of%20targeted%20killings%20in%20Kashmir%20this%20year.%20The%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20that%20Kumar%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20terrorists%20and%20the%20area%20was%20cordoned%20off%20after%20the%20attack.%20However%2C%20no%20further%20details%20have%20been%20shared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKumar%E2%80%99s%20killing%20has%20sent%20a%20wave%20of%20grief%20and%20shock%20among%20more%20than%20three%20dozen%20migrant%20workers%20who%20live%20along%20with%20their%20families%20in%20the%20many%20shanty%20hutments%20made%20of%20raw%20bricks%20that%20have%20come%20up%20in%20rows%20inside%20the%20premises%20of%20the%20brick%20kiln.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhat%20purpose%20will%20his%20killing%20serve%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Prem%20Shankar%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20who%20also%20works%20at%20the%20brick%20kiln%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20poor%20labourers.%20We%20come%20here%20so%20that%20our%20families%20don%E2%80%99t%20die%20of%20hunger.%20He%20was%20earning%20to%20feed%20his%20small%20children.%20He%20was%20not%20committing%20any%20crime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210239%2FIMG_1395.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210239%2FIMG_1395.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210239%2FIMG_1395-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210239%2FIMG_1395-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682573%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20migrant%20worker%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20breaks%20down%20while%20speaking%20with%20media%20at%20a%20brick%20kiln%20in%20Pulwama%20district.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20independent%20estimates%2C%20around%2010%20lakh%20labourers%20come%20to%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20and%20Ladakh%20every%20year%20to%20work%20in%20real%20estate%2C%20agriculture%20and%20other%20services-driven%20sectors.%20The%20migration%20starts%20at%20the%20onset%20of%20spring%20and%20ends%20before%20the%20winter%20chill%20sets%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20no%20jobs%20back%20home%2C%20so%20we%20come%20here%20to%20make%20some%20earnings.%20Even%20though%20the%20situation%20is%20not%20good%2C%20we%20get%20good%20wages%20here%20which%20is%20sufficient%20to%20keep%20us%20going.%20But%20we%20had%20never%20thought%20that%20something%20like%20this%20would%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Ram%20Kumar%2C%20a%20worker%20at%20the%20brick%20kiln.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERajesh%20Kumar%2C%20a%20manpower%20contractor%20who%20had%20facilitated%20the%20fireman%E2%80%99s%20job%20for%20Kumar%2C%20said%20that%20the%20slain%20worker%E2%80%99s%20uncle%20also%20works%20at%20a%20brick%20kiln%20in%20a%20nearby%20village.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20his%20family.%20The%20body%20was%20taken%20by%20police%20for%20post-mortem%20examination%20after%20which%20preparations%20will%20be%20made%20to%20send%20it%20to%20his%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20killing%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20seem%20to%20have%20daunted%20the%20spirits%20of%20other%20migrant%20workers%20who%20work%20at%20the%20kiln.%20A%20new%20fireman%20has%20replaced%20Kumar%20already%20and%20he%20is%20filling%20the%20fuel%20feed%20holes%20of%20the%20kiln%20with%20more%20carbon%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210810%2FIMG_1403-1.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210810%2FIMG_1403-1.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210810%2FIMG_1403-1-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30210810%2FIMG_1403-1-1024x768.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682576%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20fireman%20adding%20fuel%20to%20the%20brick%20kiln%20in%20Pulwama%20after%20one%20of%20the%20workers%20there%20was%20killed%20in%20a%20suspected%20militant%20attack%20on%20Monday.%20Photo%3A%20The%20Wire.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20work%20has%20to%20go%20on.%20If%20we%20fall%20behind%20in%20production%2C%20it%20will%20affect%20our%20earnings%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20fireman%2C%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20be%20named.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20targeted%20attack%20in%20Pulwama%20was%20the%20second%20such%20incident%20in%20Kashmir%20within%2024%20hours.%20On%20Sunday%2C%20Masroor%20Ali%20Wani%2C%20a%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20inspector%2C%20was%20shot%20multiple%20times%20and%20critically%20injured%20in%20a%20targeted%20attack%20in%20the%20capital%20Srinagar%20when%20he%20was%20reportedly%20playing%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Resistance%20Front%2C%20which%20officials%20believe%20is%20an%20offshoot%20of%20Lashkar-e-Toiba%2C%20had%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20attack.%20Wani%20is%20battling%20for%20life%20at%20Srinagar%E2%80%99s%20Sher-e-Kashmir%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20his%20condition%20remains%20critical%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReacting%20to%20the%20attack%20on%20the%20police%20officer%2C%20the%20outgoing%20director%20general%20of%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%2C%20Dilbag%20Singh%2C%20said%20the%20security%20forces%20%E2%80%9Chave%20to%20remain%20cautious%20as%20threats%20remain%E2%80%9D%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20can%E2%80%99t%20take%20things%20lightly%2C%E2%80%9D%20DGP%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20retiring%20on%20October%2031%2C%20told%20reporters%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20official%20data%2C%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20security%20personnel%20and%2010%20civilians%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20suspected%20militant%20attacks%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESecurity%20forces%20have%20also%20gunned%20down%20more%20than%2070%20militants%20in%20the%20Union%20territory%20this%20year%20with%20official%20estimates%20suggesting%20that%20more%20than%20100%20militants%20are%20active%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20many%20of%20them%20believed%20to%20be%20foreigners.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20J%26amp%3BK%E2%80%99s%20Lieutenant%20Governor%20Manoj%20Sinha%20condemned%20the%20killing%20of%20the%20migrant%20worker%2C%C2%A0saying%20it%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20not%20go%20unpunished%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20despicable%20and%20cowardly%20terrorist%20attack%20in%20Pulwama.%20Heartfelt%20condolences%20to%20the%20family%20of%20Mukesh%20Kumar.%20We%20are%20firmly%20resolved%20to%20eliminate%20the%20terrorist%20menace%20that%20continues%20to%20receive%20encouragement%20and%20reinforcement%20from%20across%20the%20border%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%C2%A0said%20in%20a%20message.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698680037000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30205921%2FThe-Wire-61.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpulwama-migrant-worker-shot-dead-second-targeted-attack-in-24-hours-in-kashmir%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20brick%20kiln%20worker%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Unnao%20district%20has%20become%20the%20first%20non-local%20casualty%20of%20targeted%20killings%20in%20Kashmir%20this%20year.%20The%20J%26amp%3BK%20Police%20said%20that%20Mukesh%20Kumar%20(45)%20was%20gunned%20down%20by%20terrorists.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fpulwama-migrant-worker-shot-dead-second-targeted-attack-in-24-hours-in-kashmir%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Israel's%20Netanyahu%20condemns%20'cruel'%20Hamas%20video%20of%20Israeli%20hostages%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698679958000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F5B64%2Fproduction%2F_131569332_05a849d9c89adc57e2e8a0daa4f8d9c567c372bb.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67265915%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Footage%20shows%20three%20female%20hostages%20berating%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%20for%20failing%20to%20secure%20their%20release.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A33%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67265915%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67265915.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-67265915.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IIT%20Guwahati%20Invents%20Sensor%20That%20Helps%20Diabetics%20Choose%20Low%20Glycemic%20Index%20Foods%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENishita%20(40)%20was%20diagnosed%20with%20diabetes%20more%20than%20eight%20years%20back.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20through%20childbirth%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331532%2Ftherapy-in-chennai-mental-health-cafe-wellness-centre-pooja-srinivasa-love-hope-company%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epostpartum%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20various%20stages%20of%20her%20career%2C%20the%20young%20banker%20based%20in%20Mumbai%20dealt%20with%20fluctuating%20blood%20sugar%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20regain%20some%20control%20over%20her%20health%2C%20she%20started%20with%20just%20a%20workout%20but%20found%20it%20hard%20to%20control%20the%20sugar%20spikes.%20Working%20with%20a%20dietician%20and%20doing%20a%20deep%20dive%20into%20what%20is%20really%20needed%20to%20manage%20life%20as%20a%20Type%202%20diabetic%2C%20Nishita%20found%20the%20secret%20sauce%20to%20be%20a%20combination%20of%20working%20out%2C%20a%20rich%20diet%2C%20and%20managing%20stress.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%20her%20day%20starts%20with%20a%2045-minute%20walk%2Frun%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20breakfast%20of%20millet%20%3Cem%3Eupma%2Fdosa%2Fidli%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20glass%20of%20black%20coffee.%20Lunch%20is%20a%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%2Fbajra%20bhakri%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread)%20with%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20salad%2C%20dal%20and%20%3Cem%3Esubzi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(cooked%20vegetables).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20keeps%20her%20dinner%20light%2C%20with%20soup%2C%20salad%20and%20an%20occasional%20whole%20wheat%20roti%2Fbrown%20bread%20or%20some%20quinoa.%20Staying%20away%20from%20our%20usual%20staples%20like%20rice%2Fwhole%20wheat%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread)%2C%20and%20completely%20avoiding%20junk%20food%20and%20sugar%2C%20has%20helped%20her%20keep%20her%20blood%20sugar%20under%20control%2C%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELike%20Nishita%2C%20several%20Indians%20live%20with%20diabetes%20every%20day%2C%20making%20India%20infamous%20for%20being%20the%20%E2%80%98diabetes%20capital%E2%80%99%20of%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20study%20published%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thelancet.com%2Fjournals%2Flandia%2Farticle%2FPIIS2213-8587(23)00119-5%2Ffulltext%5C%22%3EThe%20Lancet%20Diabetes%20and%20Endocrinology%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20India%20has%20more%20than%20101%20million%20people%20living%20with%20diabetes.%20Another%20concerning%20finding%20in%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%E2%80%93India%20Diabetes%20(ICMR-INDIAB)%20study%20was%20the%20fact%20that%2015.3%25%20of%20the%20population%20is%20pre-diabetic.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20is%20the%20case%20with%20many%20illnesses%2C%20diabetes%20is%20directly%20linked%20with%20being%20a%20lifestyle%20disease%2C%20which%20is%20often%20an%20outcome%20of%20poor%20diet%2C%20work-life%20balance%20other%20than%20being%20genetic.%20The%20key%20to%20managing%20such%20diseases%20is%20managing%20its%20symptoms%20and%20our%20approach%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Glycemic%20Index%20(GI)%20is%20a%20rating%20system%20used%20to%20classify%20foods%20that%20are%20safe%20to%20eat%20from%20a%20blood%20sugar%20perspective.%20It%20is%20a%20measure%20of%20how%20quickly%20a%20food%20can%20make%20your%20blood%20sugar%20(glucose)%20rise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETo%20help%20diabetic%20patients%20live%20an%20easier%20and%20stress-free%20life%2C%20the%20researchers%20from%20the%20Indian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20Guwahati%20(IIT-Guwahati)%20have%20developed%20a%20device%20to%20instantly%20detect%20the%20glycemic%20levels%20in%20food.%20This%20sensor%20can%20determine%20the%20GI%20of%20different%20food%20sources%20in%20real-time%20which%20is%20crucial%20for%20diabetes%20management.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDisease%20management%20becomes%20crucial%2C%20and%20an%20important%20part%20of%20that%2C%20especially%20for%20diabetics%2C%20is%20knowing%20the%20glycemic%20index%20of%20what%20they%20eat%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Professor%20Dipankar%20Bandyopadhyay%20of%20IIT%20Guwahati%2C%20one%20of%20people%20from%20the%20research%20team%20behind%20this%20important%20innovation%20of%20the%20department%20of%20chemical%20engineering%2C%20along%20with%20Prathu%20Raja%20Parmar%2C%20who%20explained%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20what%20went%20into%20this%20Point-Of-Care-Testing%20(POCT)%20prototype.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20the%20sensor%20took%20birth%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPrototype-for-the-device-1698672520.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Prototype%20of%20the%20device%20developed%20by%20IIT%20Guwahati%20researchers.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPrototype-for-the-device-1698672520.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPrototype-for-the-device-1698672520-300x169.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPrototype-for-the-device-1698672520-500x281.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPrototype-for-the-device-1698672520-768x432.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FPrototype-for-the-device-1698672520-150x84.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333225%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPrototype%20of%20the%20device%20developed%20by%20IIT%20Guwahati%20researchers.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202014-15%2C%20Nestle%20India%20was%20in%20a%20soup%20when%20food%20safety%20regulators%20found%20that%20Maggi%20Noodles%20had%20high%20levels%20of%20monosodium%20glutamate%20(MSG)%20along%20with%20lead%2C%20which%20was%20much%20above%20permissible%20levels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrathu%2C%20who%20has%20a%20food%20engineering%20background%20and%20is%20pursuing%20his%20research%20on%20different%20issues%20in%20food%2C%20started%20researching%20lead%20contamination%20in%20rice%20and%20other%20starch%20sources.%20It%20was%20his%20research%20on%20the%20synthesis%20of%20nanoparticles%20in%20different%20foods%20that%20led%20them%20to%20innovating%20this%20sensor%20for%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20controversy%20then%20about%20lead%20and%20arsenic%20contamination%20in%20rice%20and%20other%20starch%20sources%20in%20fast%20foods.%20While%20working%20on%20that%2C%20we%20found%20that%20the%20other%20major%20aspect%20was%20the%20glycemic%20nature%20of%20these%20starch%20sources.%20We%20wanted%20to%20create%20awareness%20on%20the%20GI%20of%20these%20fast%20food%20items%20which%20are%20consumed%20so%20much%20by%20the%20younger%20generations%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Professor%20Dipankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20sensor%20was%20developed%20at%20IIT-Guwahati%E2%80%99s%20sensor%20hub.%20While%20some%20sensors%20work%20on%20disease%20identification%2C%20this%20one%20works%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F325105%2Fhyderabad-entrepreneur-raju-bhupati-makes-affordable-troo-good-millet-snacks%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisease%20mitigation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20explains%20the%20professor.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CComplications%20due%20to%20diabetes%2C%20like%20chronic%20kidney%20and%20liver%20diseases%2C%20really%20affect%20the%20quality%20of%20life.%20We%20want%20to%20show%20the%20correlation%20of%20junk%20food%20to%20GI%20to%20help%20the%20next%20generation%20become%20free%20of%20diabetes.%20One%20can%20follow%20a%20personalised%20diet%20thanks%20to%20our%20high%20precision%20sensor%20and%20manage%20diabetes%20better%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20the%20role%20of%20GI%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FResearchers-working-on-the-device-prototype-1698672519.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22This%20device%20can%20help%20in%20diabetic%20management.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FResearchers-working-on-the-device-prototype-1698672519.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FResearchers-working-on-the-device-prototype-1698672519-300x179.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FResearchers-working-on-the-device-prototype-1698672519-500x298.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FResearchers-working-on-the-device-prototype-1698672519-768x458.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FResearchers-working-on-the-device-prototype-1698672519-1536x917.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FResearchers-working-on-the-device-prototype-1698672519-150x90.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333224%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22955%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThis%20device%20can%20help%20in%20diabetic%20management.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20explains%20that%20high-GI%20foods%20stimulate%20an%20increased%20demand%20for%20insulin%2C%20contributing%20to%20the%20risk%20of%20developing%20type-2%20diabetes%2C%20while%20low-GI%20food%20helps%20to%20prevent%20diabetes%2C%20heart%20disease%20and%20obesity.%20Foods%20with%20low%20GI%20increase%20glucose%20slowly%20and%20can%20help%20you%20control%20your%20blood%20sugar.%20High%20GI%20foods%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20increase%20blood%20glucose%20quickly%20and%20make%20it%20very%20hard%20to%20control%20diabetes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20three%20major%20components%20in%20the%20food%20we%20consume%20%E2%80%93%20carbohydrates%2C%20fats%20and%20proteins.%20A%20large%20part%20of%20Indian%20food%20consists%20of%20carbohydrates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCarbohydrates%20contain%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20starch.%20Starch%20gets%20broken%20down%20into%20glucose%2C%20which%20we%20then%20burn%20to%20generate%20energy%20for%20work.%20The%20scientific%20name%20of%20starch%20is%20amylose%2C%20which%20is%20broken%20down%20by%20an%20enzyme%20called%20amylase%20to%20maltose%20(small%20chain%20sugars)%2C%20before%20getting%20converted%20to%20glucose%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Professor%20Dipankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20adds%20that%20there%20are%20three%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F304454%2Ftwo-friends-climate-tech-startup-climes-helps-neutralise-carbon-footprint%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edifferent%20types%20of%20starches%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20digest%20differently%20and%20knowing%20which%20food%20item%20contains%20which%20starch%2C%20can%20transform%20the%20way%20you%20manage%20your%20diabetes.%20The%20three%20types%20are%20%E2%80%93%20Rapidly%20Digestible%20Starch%20(RDS)%2C%20Slowly%20Digesting%20Starch%20(SDS)%20and%20Resistant%20Starch%20(RS).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CRDS%20is%20easily%20digested%20and%20is%20found%20in%20highly%20glycemic%20food%2C%20which%20can%20increase%20your%20blood%20glucose%20level.%20Fast%20foods%20like%20noodles%2C%20crackers%20and%20biscuits%20contain%20a%20lot%20of%20RDS.%20SDS%20takes%20time%20for%20digestion%20and%20will%20not%20increase%20your%20glucose%20level%20immediately.%20It%20can%20help%20mitigate%20diabetes.%20RS%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20get%20digested%20easily%2C%20keeps%20your%20stomach%20full%20and%20helps%20in%20diabetes%20management%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENishita%20says%20that%20the%20game%20changer%20in%20her%20life%20was%20when%20she%20found%20out%20about%20tracking%20GI%20and%20started%20her%20research%20on%20which%20food%20helps%20her%20the%20best.%20%E2%80%9CNot%20all%20carbohydrates%20are%20bad.%20Some%20make%20your%20blood%20sugar%20shoot%20up%2C%20while%20others%20work%20slowly.%20GI%20assigns%20a%20number%20to%20these%20foods%20and%20shows%20how%20fast%20a%20particular%20food%20item%20increases%20your%20blood%20glucose%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Dipankar%20adds%20that%20since%20there%20is%20a%20need%20for%20large-scale%20diabetes%20mitigation%2C%20they%20wanted%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20classify%20various%20sources%20of%20food%20to%20help%20diabetics%20avoid%20those%20items%20for%20better%20management.%20He%20adds%20that%20seeing%20the%20trend%20of%20increased%20fast-food%20consumption%2C%20they%20felt%20the%20need%20for%20a%20portable%20device%20that%20could%20immediately%20isolate%20high-glycemic%20foods.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDetecting%20GI%20in%20five%20minutes%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Point-Of-Care-Testing%20(POCT)%20prototype%20developed%20by%20the%20IIT-Guwahati%20team%20can%20detect%20the%20GI%20of%20common%20food%20sources%20in%20real-time%20with%20the%20help%20of%20a%20high-performance%20nano%20bio-sensor%20indigenously%20developed%20by%20the%20IIT-Guwahati%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPrathu%20explains%20that%20all%20we%20need%20to%20do%20is%20dispense%20a%20drop%20of%20the%20food%20source%20on%20the%20sensor.%20It%20will%20tell%20you%20whether%20it%20contains%20RDS%2C%20SDS%20or%20RS%20using%20an%20electrochemical%20sensor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20classify%20the%20food%20before%20eating%20it%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20high%20GI%20or%20low%20GI.%20You%20can%20find%20out%20right%20at%20the%20source.%20Say%20you%20are%20preparing%20a%20%3Cem%3Eroti%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20you%20can%20test%20this%20with%20the%20dough%20itself%20and%20know%20if%20it%20will%20spike%20your%20blood%20glucose%20or%20not%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20adds%20that%20when%20they%20tested%20the%20device%20on%20fast%20foods%20like%20crackers%2C%20biscuits%2C%20chips%20and%20bread%2C%20they%20found%20that%20crackers%20had%20the%20most%20RDS%2C%20followed%20by%20potato%20chips%20and%20then%20brown%20bread.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNotably%2C%20the%20SDS%2FRS%20of%20brown%20bread%20releases%20maltose%20slowly%2C%20causing%20a%20gradual%20increase%20in%20glucose%20levels%20and%20a%20lower%20response%20from%20insulin%20in%20the%20body%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Professor%20Dipankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20sensor%20is%20made%20of%20gold%20nanoparticles%20coated%20with%20amylase%2C%20the%20same%20enzyme%20that%20digests%20carbohydrates%20in%20our%20bodies.%20This%20amylase%20breaks%20the%20starch%20in%20the%20food%20into%20maltose.%20The%20sensor%20detects%20how%20much%20maltose%20is%20produced.%20The%20amount%20of%20maltose%20produced%20is%20then%20electrochemically%20detected%20to%20classify%20the%20food%20sources%20into%20RDS%2C%20SDS%20and%20RS.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Dipankar%20and%20Prathu%2C%20along%20with%20other%20researchers%20on%20their%20team%20%E2%80%93%20Jiwajyoti%20Mahanta%2C%20Saurabh%20Dubey%2C%20Tapas%20Kumar%20Mandal%20%E2%80%93%20have%20filed%20a%20patent%20for%20their%20real-time%20glycemic%20index%20sensor.%20The%20research%20findings%20have%20also%20been%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20of%20Sustainable%20Chemistry%20%26amp%3B%20Engineering%20by%20the%20American%20Chemical%20Society.%20The%20research%2C%20which%20took%20over%20five%20years%2C%20has%20been%20funded%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Electronics%20and%20Information%20Technology%20(MeitY)%20and%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20team%20wants%20to%20translate%20their%20research%20into%20a%20final%20product%2C%20which%20would%20be%20a%20point%20of%20care%20testing%20device.%20Their%20goal%20is%20to%20lower%20the%20disease%20burden%20of%20diabetes%20in%20our%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20classify%20vegetarian%20and%20non-vegetarian%20food%20with%20a%20green%20and%20red%20dot.%20You%20immediately%20know%20which%20food%20is%20vegetarian%20or%20not.%20Similarly%2C%20our%20final%20goal%20is%20the%20point%20of%20care%20testing%20device%2C%20which%20will%20convey%20at%20the%20source%20level%2C%20to%20your%20mobile%2C%20whether%20the%20food%20is%20good%20for%20diabetes%20management%20or%20not.%20You%20will%20get%20a%20message%20on%20your%20phone%20whether%20it%20is%20in%20the%20red%20zone%2C%20yellow%20zone%20or%20green%20zone%20for%20diabetics.%20We%20want%20this%20device%20to%20help%20in%20colour%20coding%20foods%20according%20to%20their%20glycemic%20index.%20Knowing%20which%20food%20is%20good%20for%20diabetics%20should%20be%20that%20easy%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Professor%20Dipankar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENishita%20sounds%20thrilled%20by%20the%20idea%20as%20well.%20She%20says%20that%20knowing%20this%20would%20make%20life%20very%20easy%20for%20diabetics%20like%20her.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20I%E2%80%99m%20able%20to%20find%20out%20if%20a%20food%20has%20a%20low%20or%20high%20GI%20at%20the%20source%2C%20it%20would%20be%20great.%20I%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20what%20I%E2%80%99m%20consuming%20then%20and%20calculate%20the%20GI%20myself.%20This%20will%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303740%2Fresearcher-quits-job-to-build-non-invasve-device-to-detect-breast-cancer-thermalytix-niramai%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprecise%20information%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20actually%20tell%20you%20if%20a%20food%20item%2C%20which%20we%20consume%20outside%20or%20at%20home%2C%20is%20good%20for%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3