tten%20promises%20he%20made%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202018%20Chhattisgarh%20Assembly%20polls.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%2C%20the%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20took%20a%20swipe%20at%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20in%20the%20state%20and%20alleged%20tainted%20money%20from%20the%20liquor%20scam%20was%20being%20invested%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20seeing%20some%20rallies%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20and%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%2C%20I%20am%20reminded%20of%20the%20(2008)%20film%20Ghajini.%20They%20are%20suffering%20from%20memory%20loss.%20They%20have%20forgotten%20what%20they%20promised%20in%20the%20past%20(in%20the%202018%20poll%20campaign)%20and%20have%20started%20lying%20afresh%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMr%20Fadnavis%20claimed%20the%20Baghel%20government%20helped%20in%20the%20making%20of%20fake%20holograms%2C%20that%20are%20put%20on%20liquor%20bottles%2C%20and%20earned%20Rs%202%2C000%20crore%2C%20which%20is%20now%20being%20invested%20in%20the%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20asking%20about%20the%20Congress'%20promise%20of%20prohibition%20but%20they%20(party)%20don't%20remember%20it%20anymore.%20The%20Congress%20promised%20to%20start%20an%20air%20ambulance%2C%20but%20are%20unable%20to%20run%20normal%20ambulance%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20alleged%20PSC%20(Public%20Service%20Commission)%20scam%2C%20Mr%20Fadnvais%20taunted%20that%20Chhattisgarh%20is%20the%20first%20state%20where%20one%20needs%20to%20be%20the%20children%20of%20politicians%20and%20bureaucrats%20to%20get%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20had%20heard%20someone%20had%20consumed%20chara%20(fodder)%20in%20Bihar.%20But%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20they%20consumed%20'gobar'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20targeting%20the%20Baghel%20government%20over%20alleged%20corruption%20in%20the%20cow%20dung%20procurement%20scheme.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BModi%20government%20had%20launched%20welfare%20schemes%20for%20the%20poor%20but%20the%20Baghel%20government%20stopped%20the%20construction%20of%20houses%20for%20them.%20They%20(Congress%20government)%20claim%20they%20will%20bring%20new%20schemes%20for%20the%20construction%20of%20houses%2C%20which%20is%20never%20going%20to%20happen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20promise%20of%20giving%20subsidy%20of%20Rs%20500%20on%20LPG%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Mr%20Fadnvais%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BModi%20ji%20is%20already%20giving%20subsidy%20of%20Rs%20400%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThey%20(Congress)%20procure%20paddy%20from%20farmers%20for%20which%20they%20take%20Rs%202200%20(per%20quintal)%20from%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20but%20then%20take%20credit%20for%20the%20entire%20procurement%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Mr%20Fadnavis%20addressed%20an%20election%20rally%20in%20Dhamtari%20city%20and%20accused%20the%20Baghel%20government%20of%20indulging%20in%20scams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAssembly%20polls%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20will%20be%20held%20in%20two%20phases%20on%20November%207%20and%2017%2C%20while%20results%20will%20be%20declared%20on%20December%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698675540000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-10%2Fseh5rddo_rahul-gandhi-1200_625x300_30_October_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-rahul-has-forgotten-his-promises-reminds-me-of-film-ghajini-mocks-fadnavis-4528695%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Devendra%20Fadnavis%20on%20Monday%20said%20rallies%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20reminded%20him%20of%20Hindi%20film%20%26quot%3BGhajini%26quot%3B%2C%20in%20which%20the%20main%20character%20suffers%20from%20short%20term%20memory%20loss%2C%20as%20the%20latter%20has%20forgotten%20promises%20he%20made%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202018%20polls.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-rahul-has-forgotten-his-promises-reminds-me-of-film-ghajini-mocks-fadnavis-4528695%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-rahul-has-forgotten-his-promises-reminds-me-of-film-ghajini-mocks-fadnavis-4528695%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-rahul-has-forgotten-his-promises-reminds-me-of-film-ghajini-mocks-fadnavis-4528695%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tatas%20Can%20Recover%20Rs%20766%20Crore%20From%20Bengal%20For%20Singur%20Investment%3A%20Panel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Bengal%20government%20has%20to%20pay%20Tata%20Motors%20a%20massive%20sum%20of%20Rs%20765.78%20crore%20with%2011%20per%20cent%20interest%20from%20September%202016%20for%20the%20closure%20of%20its%20Nano%20factory%20in%20Singur%2C%20the%20company%20said%20today.%20The%20unanimous%20decision%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20company%20came%20from%20a%20three-member%20Arbitral%20Tribunal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20regard%20to%20the%20automobile%20manufacturing%20facility%20at%20Singur%20(West%20Bengal)%2C%20this%20is%20to%20inform%20that%20the%20aforesaid%20pending%20Arbitral%20proceedings%20before%20a%20three-member%20Arbitral%20Tribunal%20has%20now%20been%20finally%20disposed%20of%20by%20a%20unanimous%20Award%20dated%20October%2030%2C%202023%20in%20favour%20of%20TML%20whereby%20Tata%20Motors%20has%20been%20held%20to%20be%20entitled%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20respondent%20(WBIDC)%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%20765.78%20crore%20with%20interest%20thereon%20%40%2011%25%20p.a.%20from%20September%201%2C%202016%20till%20actual%20recovery%20thereof%2C%26quot%3B%20Tata%20Motors%20said%20in%20a%20note%20to%20the%20National%20Stock%20Exchange.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTata%20Motors%20has%20also%20been%20held%20to%20be%20entitled%20to%20recover%20from%20the%20respondent%20(WBIDC)%20a%20sum%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20towards%20cost%20of%20the%20proceedings%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20note%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETatas%20had%20to%20abandon%20the%20Nano%20factory%20it%20planned%20in%20Bengal%20in%202008%20and%20shift%20it%20to%20Gujarat%20following%20incessant%20protests%20spearheaded%20by%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20--%20who%20was%20then%20in%20the%20Opposition%20--%20and%20her%20Trinamool%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAfter%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20the%20Trinamool%20government%20had%20offered%20Tatas%20alternative%20land%20for%20a%20factory.%20But%20the%20company%20had%20refused%2C%20saying%20it%20would%20prefer%20a%20compensation%20of%20Rs%20154%20crore%20which%20it%20paid%20the%20Left%20Front%20government%20to%20acquire%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20ruled%20the%20Left%20Front%20government's%20decision%20to%20acquire%20land%20in%20Singur%20%26quot%3Bgrossly%20perverse%20and%20illegal%26quot%3B%20in%20view%20of%20non-compliance%20with%20provisions%20of%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETata%20Motors%20had%20defended%20the%20acquisition%2C%20contending%20that%20the%20government%20could%20not%20change%20its%20stance%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20lawsuit%20just%20because%20a%20different%20political%20party%20had%20come%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20government%20could%20do%20so%20if%20there%20is%20evidence%20that%20the%20acquisition%20was%20illegal.%20Tata%20then%20sought%20arbitration%20under%20its%20lease%20agreement%20with%20the%20state%20government%20that%20included%20it%20as%20a%20dispute-resolution%20mechanism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Left%20Front%20had%20acquired%20agricultural%20land%20in%20Singur%20for%20the%20Nano%20factory%2C%20showcasing%20the%20Nano%20project%20as%20the%20beginning%20of%20a%20policy%20shift%20to%20industrialise%20the%20state%20and%20boost%20its%20dying%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698675420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2020-03%2F2vekhh2_tata-motors_625x300_02_March_20.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftatas-can-recover-rs-766-crore-from-bengal-for-singur-investment-panel-4528547%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bengal%20government%20has%20to%20pay%20Tata%20Motors%20a%20massive%20sum%20of%20Rs%20765.78%20crore%20with%2011%20per%20cent%20interest%20from%20September%202016%20for%20the%20closure%20of%20its%20Nano%20factory%20in%20Singur%2C%20the%20company%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftatas-can-recover-rs-766-crore-from-bengal-for-singur-investment-panel-4528547%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftatas-can-recover-rs-766-crore-from-bengal-for-singur-investment-panel-4528547%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftatas-can-recover-rs-766-crore-from-bengal-for-singur-investment-panel-4528547%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tata%20Motors%20wins%20Singur%20land%20case%2C%20entitled%20to%20recover%20Rs%20766%20cr%20from%20WB%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698675288000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2022-06%2F27%2Ffull%2F1656301005-7259.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Ftata-motors-wins-singur-land-case-entitled-to-recover-rs-766-cr-from-wb-123103001049_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tata%20Motors%20had%20to%20shift%20its%20plant%20to%20produce%20small%20car%20Nano%20from%20Singur%20in%20West%20Bengal%20to%20Sanand%20in%20Gujarat%20in%20October%202008%20due%2