D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Both%20Congress%2C%20BJP%20Failed%20Chhattisgarh's%20Adivasis%3A%20Veteran%20Tribal%20Leader%20Arvind%20Netam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30191819%2FScreenshot-2023-10-30-at-7.16.44%25E2%2580%25AFPM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Former%20Union%20minister%20and%20veteran%20tribal%20leader%20Arvind%20Netam%20has%20accused%20both%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20of%20failing%20the%20Adivasis%20of%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20which%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9Cforced%E2%80%9D%20him%20to%20quit%20the%20former%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eform%20his%20new%20political%20outfit%2C%20the%20Hamar%20Raj%20Party.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%2C%20who%20heads%20the%20Sarva%20Adivasi%20Samaj%2C%20an%20umbrella%20organisation%20of%20tribal%20groups%20in%20the%20state%2C%20announced%20in%20September%20that%20the%20body%20had%20registered%20a%20political%20party%20under%20the%20name%20of%20Hamar%20Raj%20Party.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20316px)%2085vw%2C%20316px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22316%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-300x248.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F26081310%2FIMG_2711-1024x845.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-681756%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22260%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20tribal%20communities%20constituting%20about%2030%25%20of%20Chhattisgarh%E2%80%99s%20population%2C%20Netam%E2%80%99s%20party%20could%20spring%20a%20surprise%20in%20a%20state%20that%20has%20traditionally%20seen%20straight%20battles%20between%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%20said%20that%20he%20resigned%20from%20the%20Congress%20as%20it%20was%20no%20longer%20the%20party%20it%20was%20under%20Indira%20Gandhi%20and%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CSarva%20Adivasi%20Samaj%20has%20been%20raising%20issues%20of%20the%20Adivasis%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20with%20different%20governments%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20the%20Congress%20government%20or%20the%20BJP%20government.%20But%20you%20will%20be%20surprised%20that%20under%20the%20BJP%20government%20that%20ruled%20the%20state%20for%2015%20years%20and%20then%20the%20Congress%20government%20(which%20is%20in%20power%20now)%2C%20neither%20paid%20any%20heed%20to%20our%20demands.%20In%20fact%2C%20they%20did%20not%20even%20bother%20calling%20us%20for%20a%20discussion%20even%20once.%20After%20a%20lot%20of%20frustration%2C%20we%20decided%20that%20if%20there%20is%20no%20one%20to%20listen%20to%20us%2C%20then%20where%20should%20one%20go%20in%20a%20democracy%3F%20These%20parties%20are%20only%20interested%20in%20garnering%20votes.%20We%20were%20forced%20to%20form%20the%20party.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20wanted%20Sarva%20Adivasi%20Samaj%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20electoral%20democracy%2C%20but%20what%20can%20be%20done%3F%20Both%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress%20are%20the%20same%2C%20so%20where%20will%20Adivasi%20%3Cem%3Esamaj%3C%2Fem%3E%20go%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%20served%20as%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20education%20and%20social%20welfare%20in%20the%20Indira%20Gandhi%20government%20and%20as%20the%20Union%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20agriculture%20under%20P.V.%20Narasimha%20Rao.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20veteran%20Congress%20leader%2C%20however%2C%20has%20had%20several%20run-ins%20with%20the%20party.%20In%201997%2C%20he%20joined%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20after%20he%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feconomy-policy%2Fpressure-on-digvijay-as-arvind-netam-joins-bsp-197041501106_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edenied%20a%20ticket%20in%20the%201996%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20but%20returned%20to%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Findepth%2Farvind-netam-13235%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECongress%20in%201998%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%202012%2C%20he%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Flatest-news%2Fnetam-suspended-from-congress-for-p-a-sangma%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esuspended%20from%20the%20Congress%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20after%20he%20supported%20P.A.%20Sangma%E2%80%99s%20presidential%20candidature.%20He%20rejoined%20the%20Congress%20in%202018%20before%20that%20year%E2%80%99s%20Chhattisgarh%20assembly%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%20said%20that%20his%20Hamar%20Raj%20party%20will%20contest%20about%2050%20of%20the%2090%20seats%20in%20the%20elections%20next%20month%2C%20mostly%20on%20the%20reserved%20seats%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%2C%20and%20highlight%20issues%20of%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20jal%2C%20jungle%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(water%2C%20forest%20and%20land).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20main%20issue%20is%20%E2%80%98%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Ejal%2C%20jangal%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Union%20government%20is%20making%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fconstitutionality-of-forest-conservation-act-2023-challenged-in-sc-centre-to-respond-in-6-weeks%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%20changes%20in%20the%20forest%20laws%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20We%20fought%20the%20British%20too%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20jal%2C%20jangal%2C%20zameen%2C%20didn%E2%80%99t%20we%3F%20Now%20people%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20know%20anything%20about%20tribal%20areas.%20The%20state%20forest%20minister%20has%20still%20not%20visited%20Bastar.%20Apart%20from%20for%20a%20few%20private%20programmes%2C%20neither%20has%20the%20home%20minister%20nor%20education%20minister%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Finterview-ts-singh-deo-bhupesh-baghel-chhattisgarh%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Einterview%20with%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ethis%20month%2C%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20T.S.%20Singh%20Deo%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%20government%20has%20focused%20on%20tribal%20welfare%20through%20education%20infrastructure%2C%20supporting%20cultural%20activities%20through%20government%20through%20cash%20being%20provided%20for%20the%20upkeep%20of%20centres%20of%20religious%20sentiments%2C%20and%20giving%20stipend%20to%20those%20who%20look%20after%20these%20places%20of%20worship%20and%20formulating%20ruled%20under%20the%20Panchayat%20Extension%20to%20Scheduled%20Areas%20(PESA)%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%20also%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Congress%20government%E2%80%99s%20claims%20that%20by%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fother-states%2Fchhattisgarh-govt-implements-pesa-rule-2022%2Farticle65751589.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eimplementing%20the%20extension%20of%20PESA%20Rules%202022%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20state%20last%20year%2C%20it%20had%20empowered%20gram%20sabhas.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CPESA%20was%20made%20by%20us%20in%201996.%20We%20knew%20that%20after%201991%E2%80%99s%20liberalisation%20reforms%2C%20the%20tribal%20areas%20would%20be%20vulnerable%20and%20governments%20would%20loot%20these%20areas.%20The%20objective%20of%20PESA%20was%20to%20ensure%20that%20gram%20sabhas%20should%20be%20consulted%20on%20all%20issues%20relating%20to%20j%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eal%2C%20jangal%2C%20zameen%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20Gram%20sabhas%20need%20security%20and%20protection.%20But%20gram%20sabhas%20have%20been%20reduced%20to%20advisory%20roles.%20The%20Congress%20has%20finished%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20gram%20sabha.%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20came%20here%20but%20did%20he%20speak%20about%20PESA%3F%20They%20(Congress)%20themselves%20are%20clearing%20the%20roads%20in%20Adivasi%20areas%20for%20corporate%20houses.%20Have%20any%20of%20these%20Congress%20ministers%20even%20read%20the%20PESA%20law%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20against%20industrialisation%20or%20industries.%20Yes%2C%20development%20should%20take%20place%20but%20we%20need%20to%20talk%20about%20zilla%20autonomy%20and%20empowering%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20Congress%20government%20of%20hypocrisy%20by%20raising%20allegations%20of%20crony%20capitalism%20against%20Gautam%20Adani%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20while%20doing%20business%20with%20his%20company%20in%20Congress-ruled%20states.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Bhupesh%20Baghel%20government%20is%20doing%20business%20worth%2020%2C000%20crore%20with%20Adani.%20Who%20will%20answer%20that%3F%20In%20Rajasthan%2C%20which%20is%20also%20under%20Congress%2C%20they%20are%20also%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fadani-mine-chhattisgarh-expansion-scroll%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edoing%20business%20with%20Adani%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20first%20time%2C%20residents%20of%20more%20than%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Felections%2Fchhattisgarh%2Fchhattisgarh-polls-residents-of-over-120-villages-in-maoist-hit-bastar-to-vote-in-their-own-villages-for-first-time-since-independence-2725287%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E120%20villages%20in%20Bastar%20will%20vote%20in%20their%20own%20settlements%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ein%20the%20assembly%20polls%20%E2%80%93%20which%20will%20be%20held%20in%20two%20phases%20on%20November%207%20and%2017.%20Polling%20stations%20will%20be%20set%20up%20in%20these%20erstwhile%20Maoist%20strongholds.%20The%20Congress%20and%20the%20BJP%20are%20each%20claiming%20credit%20for%20allegedly%20reducing%20Maoist%20violence%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetam%20rejected%20the%20claims.%20%E2%80%9CIrrespective%20of%20whether%20elections%20are%20taking%20place%20in%20120%20villages%20or%20not%2C%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20Naxals%20are%20still%20here%2C%20aren%E2%80%99t%20they%3F%20Over%20one%20lakh%20members%20of%20paramilitary%20forces%20are%20already%20in%20the%20state%20and%20now%20you%20are%20bringing%20in%20more.%20We%20have%20been%20asking%20for%2015%20years%20to%20call%20the%20Sarva%20Adivasi%20Samaj%20for%20talks%20but%20the%20governments%20have%20no%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ehumdardi%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E(sympathy).%20They%20don%E2%80%99t%20go%20deep%20into%20these%20tribal%20areas%20and%20don%E2%80%99t%20listen%20to%20the%20people.%20This%20is%20a%20socio-economic%20problem%20%E2%80%93%20wherever%20there%20is%20poverty%20and%20hunger%2C%20Naxals%20will%20be%20born%20there.%20Sociologists%20and%20journalists%20have%20been%20writing%20about%20this%20for%20years.%20So%20where%20is%20the%20planning%20to%20deal%20with%20this%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A