ackward%20classes%20(OBCs)%20that%20the%20Congress%20has%20adopted%20as%20its%20main%20plank%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20states%20headed%20to%20an%20assembly%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20the%20Bihar%20government%20is%20scheduled%20to%20showcase%20its%20success%20in%20providing%20jobs%20at%20an%20event%20in%20Patna%E2%80%99s%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20on%20November%202.%20Nitish%2C%20his%20deputy%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20Bihar%20education%20minister%20Chandra%20Shekhar%20and%20other%20ministers%20will%20give%20appointment%20letters%20to%201.2%20lakh%20teachers%20recruited%20through%20the%20Bihar%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(BPSC)%E2%80%99s%20examinations.%20This%20comes%20in%20the%20background%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20failing%20miserably%20on%20his%20promise%20to%20generate%201.5%20crore%20jobs%20every%20year%20before%20his%20election%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20media%20channels%20frequently%20report%20about%20fissures%20in%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20%3Ci%3EMahagathbandhan%3C%2Fi%3E%20government%2C%20the%20parties%20have%20displayed%20solid%20unity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2026%2C%20the%20Congress%20invited%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20president%20Lalu%20Prasad%20Yadav%20as%20the%20chief%20guest%20for%20the%20136th%20birth%20anniversary%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20first%20chief%20minister%2C%20Shri%20Krishna%20Sinha%2C%20at%20Sadaqat%20Ashram%20%E2%80%93%20the%20grand%20old%20party%E2%80%99s%20iconic%20office%20at%20Patna.%20The%20symbolism%20at%20the%20event%20was%20evident%3A%20Lalu%20Yadav%20continues%20to%20be%20a%20central%20cog%20in%20opposing%20Hindutva.%20Through%20the%20event%2C%20the%20Congress%20showed%20that%20it%20respected%20him%20as%20a%20champion%20of%20social%20justice%20and%20secularism.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20part%2C%20Lalu%20revealed%20that%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20and%20other%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20sent%20Akhilesh%20Singh%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Pradesh%20Congress%20Committee%2C%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20his%20advice.%20Scotching%20the%20reports%20of%20fissures%2C%20Lalu%20announced%20that%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20constituents%20would%20organise%20%3Ci%3E%E2%80%9CBhajpa%20hatao%2C%20Desh%20bachaao%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%20(Remove%20BJP%20from%20power%3B%20save%20the%20country)%20rally%20at%20the%20Gandhi%20Maidan%20to%20bring%20the%20curtain%20down%20on%20the%20era%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Amit%20Shah%20and.%20The%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20requested%20Lalu%20to%20%E2%80%9Clead%E2%80%9D%20the%20battle%20against%20the%20divisive%20forces%20in%20the%202024%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30173545%2FLalusksinhaanniversary.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30173545%2FLalusksinhaanniversary.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30173545%2FLalusksinhaanniversary-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30173545%2FLalusksinhaanniversary-1024x683.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-682536%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPhoto%3A%20By%20arrangement%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAmbedkar%20and%20Lohia%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EUnion%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20the%20spearhead%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20machine%2C%20has%20raised%20issues%20like%20the%20lynching%20of%20a%20Hindu%20youth%2C%20the%20Palestine-Israel%20conflict%2C%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20Ayodhya%20and%20Mughals%20in%20rallies%20in%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20The%20Congress%2C%20which%20is%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20main%20rival%20in%20these%20states%2C%20is%20countering%20Shah%20by%20promising%20the%20caste%20survey%20and%20proportionate%20representation%20to%20OBCs%20and%20other%20marginalised%20sections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBihar%20has%20offered%20a%20politically%20befitting%20narrative%2C%20based%20on%20solid%20performance%20and%20groundwork%2C%20to%20counter%20Hindutva%20in%20the%20election-bound%20states.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20since%20Narendra%20Modi%20ascended%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20the%20BJP%20is%20struggling%20to%20counter%20the%20strategy%20that%20Nitish%20Kumar%20has%20built%20with%20the%20backing%20of%20Lalu%2C%20Tejashwi%2C%20and%20allies%20like%20the%20Congress%20and%20Left%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAs%20murmurs%20spread%20that%20Nitish%20will%20go%20back%20to%20the%20saffron%20camp%20again%2C%20the%20CM%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20don%E2%80%99t%20care%20at%20all%20what%20they%20(BJP%20leaders)%20say.%20I%20am%20doing%20my%20work.%20It%E2%80%99s%20for%20everyone%20to%20see%20the%20work%20we%20have%20done%20in%20building%20infrastructure%2C%20empowering%20the%20women%20and%20the%20marginalised%20sections%20and%20providing%20employment%20in%20Bihar.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%2C%20devoid%20of%20its%20own%20icons%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20the%20making%20of%20India%2C%20tried%20to%20co-opt%20the%20legacies%20of%20Ram%20Manohar%20Lohia%20and%20B.R.%20Ambedkar.%20But%20Nitish%2C%20after%20parting%20ways%20with%20the%20BJP%2C%20has%20worked%20assiduously%20to%20retrieve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLohia%20and%20Ambedkar%20fought%20for%20an%20appropriate%20share%20in%20political%20structure%20and%20governance%20for%20backward%20sections%20and%20Dalits%20respectively.%20Gandhiji%E2%80%99s%2C%20Lohia%E2%80%99s%20and%20Ambedkar%E2%80%99s%20philosophies%20are%20central%20to%20our%20(RJD%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20United%E2%80%99s)%20deeds%20and%20operations%2C%20whereas%20the%20BJP%20tried%20to%20co-opt%20Lohia%20and%20Ambedkar%20to%20garner%20votes%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20RJD%20national%20spokesperson%20and%20MP%20Manoj%20Jha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20met%20and%20praised%20a%20%3Ci%3Esadhu%2C%20%3C%2Fi%3ERambhadracharya%2C%20and%20exhorted%20the%20people%20to%20adhere%20to%20his%20ideals.%20But%20the%20RJD%E2%80%99s%20net-savvy%20cadres%20made%20a%20slogan%20by%20the%20sadhu%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Ci%3EMare%20Mulayam%20Kanshi%20Ram%2C%20prem%20se%20bolo%20Jai%20Shri%20Ram%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fi%3E%20(Mulayam%20and%20Kanshi%20Ram%20are%20dead%2C%20shout%20Jai%20Shriram%20with%20more%20gusto%20now)%E2%80%9D%20viral%20and%20exposed%20his%20%E2%80%9Cnexus%E2%80%9D%20with%20Hindutva%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EBihar%3A%20Land%20of%20Revolution%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20describing%20Bihar%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cland%20of%20ushering%20in%20political%20changes%E2%80%9D%2C%20had%20proposed%20Patna%20as%20the%20venue%20of%20the%20opposition%20parties%E2%80%99%20first%20conclave%20on%20June%2023.%20It%20was%20not%20just%20rhetoric.%20Bihar%20has%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20several%20movements.%20The%20Jayaprakash%20Narayan-led%20Bihar%20movement%2C%20which%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20the%20formation%20of%20the%20first%20non-Congress%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%20in%201977%2C%20began%20in%20Bihar.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Naxalite%20movement%20that%20originated%20in%20the%20Naxalbari%20region%20of%20Bengal%20in%20the%20late%201960s%20had%20a%20prolonged%20impact%20in%20Bihar.%20The%20CPI%20ML-Liberation%20%E2%80%93%20a%20strong%20Left%20party%20at%20the%20grassroots%20level%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20product%20of%20the%20Naxalite%20movement%20and%20part%20of%20the%20%3Ci%3EMahagathbandhan%3C%2Fi%3E%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBihar%20also%20played%20a%20major%20role%20in%20what%20is%20dubbed%20the%20%E2%80%9CFirst%20War%20of%20Independence%E2%80%9D%20in%201857%2C%20with%20Veer%20Kuer%20Singh%20challenging%20the%20mighty%20British%20military.%20Apparently%2C%20the%20state%20seems%20to%20be%20playing%20a%20key%20role%20in%20countering%20Hindutva%20politics%20at%20the%20national%20level.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20author%2C%20media%20educator%2C%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20folklore.%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698669908000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30172607%2FF6h-A1CXQAAeurW.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-emerges-as-a-template-to-counter-hindutva-narrative%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20role%20played%20by%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20uniting%2028%20parties%20against%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20government's%20decision%20to%20conduct%20a%20caste%20survey%20have%20sent%20the%20saffron%20party%20on%20the%20backfoot.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-emerges-as-a-template-to-counter-hindutva-narrative%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Support%20to%20regulations%20difference%20between%20us%20and%20tech%20firms%3A%20Sameer%20Nigam%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698669573000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-10%2F27%2Ffull%2F1698416584-1744.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fspecials%2Fbs-events%2Fsupport-to-regulations-difference-between-us-and-tech-firms-sameer-nigam-123103000905_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nigam%20said%20that%20being%20an%20early%20mover%20in%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20United%20Payments%20Interface%20also%20played%20in%20their%20favour%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com