mg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F29102733%2FIMG_7832.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20educational%20institutes%2C%20the%20word%20%E2%80%9Celite%E2%80%9D%20gets%20thrown%20around%20extensively%20in%20modern%20India.%20Yet%2C%20it%20does%20not%20seem%20to%20lose%20its%20import%20as%20oft-repeated%20descriptors%20are%20wont%20to.%20It%20is%20a%20word%20born%20out%20of%20postcolonial%20aspirations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ETragically%2C%20the%20greatest%20indicator%20of%20the%20aspirational%20nature%20of%20those%20desirous%20of%20breaching%20the%20hallowed%20halls%20of%20elite%20institutes%20is%20the%20spate%20of%20suicides%20committed%20by%20young%20adults%20unable%20to%20cope%20with%20parental%20and%20academic%20pressure.%20According%20to%20certain%20estimates%2C%20nearly%20a%20quarter%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20schoolchildren%20and%20adolescents%20suffer%20from%20psychiatric%20disorders%2C%20with%20India%20also%20having%20the%20highest%20rate%20of%20suicide%20among%20its%20youth%20population.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAll%20of%20this%20is%20even%20before%20a%20student%20is%20admitted%20to%20one%20of%20the%20elite%20institutions.%20Once%20admitted%2C%20many%20students%20often%20feel%20woefully%20underprepared%20for%20the%20pressure%20and%20rigour%20that%20these%20institutes%20demand.%20However%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20the%20academic%20workload%20that%20can%20affect%20a%20fresher%E2%80%99s%20balance%20at%20elite%20institutions%20in%20India.%20The%20lack%20of%20awareness%20of%20the%20dynamics%20of%20caste%2C%20class%20and%20gender%20in%20these%20%E2%80%9Celite%E2%80%9D%20institutions%20makes%20their%20life%20more%20miserable.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20notwithstanding%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20Presidency%20%E2%80%93%20and%20its%20academic%20cousin%2C%20Jadavpur%20University%20%E2%80%93%20continue%20to%20be%20symbols%20of%20revolutionary%20and%20radical%20thinking.%20This%20is%20what%20drew%20us%20to%20these%20campuses%3A%20not%20the%20(as%20advertised)%20world-class%20faculty%2C%20not%20the%20(near%20enough)%20state-of-the-art%20equipment%20and%20certainly%20not%20the%20prospect%20of%20the%20(often%20barely%20attended)%20classes.%20What%20made%20these%20institutions%20elite%2C%20at%20least%20to%20us%20a%20decade%20ago%2C%20was%20the%20atmosphere%20that%20promised%20to%20develop%20our%20minds%20in%20ways%20we%20had%20not%20yet%20imagined.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESwapnadeep%2C%20a%2017-year-old%20boy%20from%20Nadia%2C%20abandoned%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20science%20course%20at%20a%20local%20college%20to%20pursue%20his%20dreams%20of%20Bengali%20literary%20scholarship%20at%20one%20such%20elite%20institute%20%E2%80%93%20Jadavpur%20University.%20Yet%2C%20his%20aspirations%20and%2C%20indeed%2C%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-death-swapnadeep-kundu%5C%22%3Elife%20were%20cut%20short%20as%20hostel%20seniors%2C%20referred%20to%20in%20Bengali%20as%20%E2%80%98dada%E2%80%99%20or%20elder%20brothers%2C%20decided%20to%20enact%20their%20perversions%20on%20the%20unwitting%2C%20distinctly%20non-urban%20youth%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20such%20case%20in%20Jadavpur%3B%20in%202016%2C%20a%20second-year%20philosophy%20student%2C%20Soumitra%20De%E2%80%99s%20body%2C%20was%20found%20hanging%20in%20his%20hostel%20room.%20In%20another%20case%2C%20the%20death%20of%20a%20third-year%20mechanical%20engineering%20student%2C%20Faizan%20Ahmad%2C%20at%20IIT%20Kharagpur%20raises%20many%20questions.%20Ahmad%E2%80%99s%20family%20alleged%20that%20their%20son%20had%20been%20murdered.%20Initially%2C%20it%20was%20believed%20to%20be%20a%20case%20of%20suicide%2C%20but%20later%2C%20after%20the%20second%20post-mortem%2C%20the%20Calcutta%20high%20court%20directed%20the%20special%20investigation%20team%20to%20treat%20this%20as%20a%20case%20of%20murder.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20are%20mere%20examples%20of%20an%20avalanche%20hurtling%20through%20campuses%20in%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20case%20of%20Swapnadeep%20%E2%80%93%20the%20most%20recent%20high-profile%20incident%20of%20ragging%20on%20elite%20campuses%20%E2%80%93%20typifies%20all%20aspects%20that%20are%20characteristic%20of%20similar%20cases%20across%20the%20country%3A%20senior%20students%20enjoying%20free%20reign%20inside%20hostels%2C%20the%20lackadaisical%20approach%20of%20the%20institute%20administration%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20implementation%20of%20rules%20and%20yet%2C%20a%20certain%20academic%20and%20social%20elitism%20that%20can%20only%20be%20born%20within%20a%20colonial%20framework.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Bengal%2C%20in%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20case%2C%20this%20was%20compounded%20by%20the%20issue%20of%20the%20unabashed%20ex-student%20%E2%80%98dadas%E2%80%99%20who%20are%20often%20venerated%20by%20their%20immediate%20juniors%20as%20founts%20of%20knowledge.%20Disagree%20or%20disobey%20them%2C%20and%20your%20life%20on%20campus%20can%20become%20very%20difficult.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fcities%2Fkolkata%2Fju-students-death-35-seniors-6-ex-students-involved-in-ragging-panel-8947725%2F%5C%22%3Einternal%20committee%20probing%20the%20case%20at%20Jadavpur%20University%20has%20identified%20no%20fewer%20than%2035%20seniors%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20six%20ex-students%20who%20are%20directly%20or%20indirectly%20involved%20in%20ragging%20and%20are%2C%20arguably%2C%20responsible%20for%20maintaining%20the%20environment%20which%20led%20to%20the%20death%20of%20the%20aspiring%20teenager.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20The%20same%20panel%20has%20found%20that%20the%20youth%20was%20subjected%20to%20sexual%20and%20physical%20abuse%20alongside%20mental%20harassment.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsociety%2Fjadavpur-university-ragging-patriarchy%5C%22%3EThe%20Real%20Culprit%20Behind%20the%20Death%20of%20the%20Jadavpur%20University%20Student%20is%20Patriarchy%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERagging%20on%20educational%20campuses%20is%20little%20more%20than%20ritualised%20bullying.%20It%20has%20become%20a%20sort%20of%20rite%20of%20passage%20that%20every%20fresher%20must%20go%20through%20in%20order%20to%20be%20accepted%20into%20the%20groups%2C%20cliques%20and%20coteries%20that%20existed%20within%20the%20campus.%20The%20practice%20had%20gone%20on%20for%20decades%20before%20the%20administrators%20of%20Indian%20academia%20%E2%80%93%20mandated%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20%E2%80%93%20decided%20to%20put%20in%20place%20certain%20deterrents%2C%20most%20of%20which%20have%20evidently%20not%20worked.%20The%20number%20of%20cases%20has%20only%20risen%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20and%20sometimes%20the%20lives%20of%20aspiring%20youngsters%20have%20been%20abruptly%20ended.%20According%20to%20the%20University%20Grant%20Commission%20(UGC)%2C%20there%20were%206412%20ragging%20cases%20reported%20in%20the%20past%2010%20years%20(2012-2022)%2C%20of%20which%206%2C192%20cases%20have%20been%20addressed.%20The%20number%20of%20cases%20reported%20over%20the%20past%20four%20years%20was%201%2C016%20in%202018%2C%201%2C070%20in%202019%2C%20219%20in%202020%2C%20and%20511%20in%202021.%20The%20UGC%20did%20not%20publish%20any%20data%20after%202021.%20Overall%2C%20a%20UGC%20study%20found%20that%20in%20Indian%20institutions%2040%25%20of%20students%20reported%20experiencing%20some%20ragging%2C%20and%20only%208.6%25%20of%20those%20incidents%20were%20reported.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECaste%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20it%20is%20unfortunate%20that%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ebhadraloks%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20in%20Bengal%20(and%2C%20indeed%2C%20in%20Indian)%20academia%20are%20ignorant%20about%20caste.%20Last%20year%2C%20an%20Assistant%20Professor%20of%20the%20International%20Relations%20department%20of%20Jadavpur%20University%20was%20accused%20of%20making%20casteist%20remarks%20to%20her%20OBC%20PhD%20scholar.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20In%202021%2C%20an%20assistant%20professor%20of%20Economics%20from%20Viswa%20Bharati%20University%20refused%20to%20converse%20with%20an%20SC%20student%20and%20called%20him%20%E2%80%98impure%E2%80%99.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20not%20limited%20to%20students.%20Deputy%20Registrar%20Amal%20Kumar%20Bhuiyan%20of%20Vidyasagar%20University%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20Assistant%20Registrar%20Bivore%20Das%20of%20IIEST%2C%20Shibpur%2C%20have%20also%20recently%20alleged%20caste-based%20discrimination%20against%20their%20administrative%20superiors.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20per%20data%20submitted%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20Union%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Education%2C%20Subhas%20Sarkar%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscroll.in%2Flatest%2F1053348%2F98-students-died-by-suicide-in-higher-education-institutes-since-2018-centre-tells-parliament%5C%22%3E98%20students%20died%20by%20suicide%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%20Each%20of%20these%20students%20was%20studying%20in%20central%20universities%20and%20institutes%20of%20national%20importance%20such%20as%20IITs%2C%20NITs%2C%20etc.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20MoS%20did%20not%20say%20that%20most%20of%20these%20students%20were%20from%20lower%20caste%20or%20rural%20backgrounds.%20Very%20recently%2C%20two%20students%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.edexlive.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2Fsep%2F02%2Fiit-delhi-ayush-ashna-another-sc-student-anil-kumar-dies-by-suicide-pattern-emerging-37427.html%5C%22%3EAyush%20Asna%20and%20Anil%20Kumar%2C%20from%20the%20SC%20community%2C%20died%20from%20suicide%20in%20a%20span%20of%20two%20months%20in%20IIT%2C%20Delhi%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20makes%20clear%20that%20the%20problem%20is%20undoubtedly%20a%20national%20one.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EComing%20from%20diverse%20backgrounds%2C%20our%20own%20contrasting%20experiences%20show%20that%20there%20are%20deeper%20issues%20at%20play%20on%20Indian%20campuses%2C%20especially%20elite%20ones.%20Being%20in%20touch%20with%20both%20popular%20culture%20and%20high%20art%20is%20necessary%20in%20elite%20places%20like%20the%20Presidency%20and%20Jadavpur.%20You%20had%20to%20understand%20both%20obscure%20references%20to%20Pink%20Floyd%20and%20the%20works%20of%20Bela%20Tarr.%20For%20most%20students%20outside%20the%20cosmopolitan%20world%20of%20Kolkata%2C%20neither%20were%20familiar%20names.%20For%20some%2C%20these%20were%20things%20they%20were%20not%20interested%20in.%20An%20expression%20of%20individual%20choice%20that%2C%20in%20our%20experience%2C%20was%20often%20used%20as%20a%20premise%20of%20ostracisation%20with%20the%20suggestion%20that%20such%20a%20choice%20makes%20that%20person%20unsuitable%20for%20the%20elite%20campus.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Despite%20the%20highly%20left-leaning%20gesticulations%20of%20the%20inhabitants%20of%20such%20campus%2C%20the%20fact%20that%20this%20lack%20of%20cultural%20capital%20is%20almost%20always%20a%20result%20of%20financial%20difficulties%2C%20rural%20backgrounds%20and%20traditional%20family%20structures%20is%20often%20summarily%20ignored.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENone%20of%20this%20is%20the%20fault%20of%20the%20high-achieving%20school%20student%20who%20had%20managed%20to%20breach%20the%20walls%20of%20an%20elite%20institution.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20campus%2C%20this%20meant%20ostracisation%20and%20isolation.%20The%20fear%20of%20these%20fates%20also%20prevents%20many%20victims%20from%20not%20reporting%20their%20ordeals%20to%20the%20authorities%2C%20who%2C%20themselves%2C%20often%20fail%20to%20take%20seriously%20whatever%20reports%20they%20do%20get.%20The%20usual%20explanation%20being%2C%20%E2%80%98Oh%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20a%20bit%20of%20fun.%E2%80%99%20Senior%20students%20tend%20to%20possess%20the%20safety%20net%20of%20familiarity%20with%20the%20authorities%2C%20especially%20those%20active%20on%20campus.%20Younger%20students%20will%20see%20the%20familiarity%20of%20their%20seniors%20with%20the%20faculty%20and%20feel%20that%20anything%20they%20have%20to%20say%20will%20not%20be%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20solution%20lies%20in%20properly%20inculcating%20a%20sense%20of%20humanity%20in%20students%20entering%20elite%20institutions%20before%20they%20are%20indoctrinated%20in%20the%20esoteric%20philosophies%20of%20their%20various%20subjects.%20We%20as%20a%20society%20must%20reconsider%20our%20parameters%20of%20success.%20More%20importantly%2C%20we%20must%20stop%20gaslighting%20ourselves%20into%20thinking%20that%20caste%20and%20class%20discrimination%20does%20not%20exist.%20They%20very%20much%20do%2C%20and%20for%20those%20craving%20power%20but%20not%20possessing%20any%2C%20a%20sense%20of%20class%20or%20caste%20superiority%20is%20an%20easily%20available%20stepping%20stone%20in%20climbing%20the%20ladder%20of%20oppression.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20may%20also%20be%20worth%20considering%2C%20as%20a%20society%2C%20why%20we%20remain%20obsessed%20with%20the%20concept%20of%20the%20elite.%20It%20is%20a%20symptom%20of%20our%20postcoloniality.%20It%20is%20a%20British%20idea%20worked%20into%20the%20already%20existing%20caste%20and%20class%20system%20that%20only%20one%20particular%20group%20of%20people%20within%20society%20have%20the%20right%20to%20make%20decisions%20and%20are%2C%20by%20that%20very%20virtue%2C%20inherently%20better.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESoham%20Mukherjee%20is%20a%20doctoral%20candidate%20at%20IIEST%2C%20Shibpur%2C%20Kolkata.%20Sumanta%20Roy%20is%20a%20doctoral%20candidate%2C%20Centre%20of%20Social%20Medicine%20and%20Community%20Health%2C%20JNU%2C%20New%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22