0%2C%20%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20what%20do%20you%20have%20to%20say%3F%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20not%20responded%20to%20the%20Union%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20barb.%20However%2C%20the%20party%20has%20raised%20objection%20to%20the%20BJP%20using%20photographs%20of%20the%20Ayodhya%20Ram%20Mandir%20in%20its%20posters%20and%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbhopal%2Frow-over-bjps-ram-mandir-poll-posters-cong-complains-to-ec%2Farticleshow%2F104810517.cms%5C%22%3E%20filed%20a%20complaint%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20this%20regard.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERam%20temple%20billboards%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBillboards%20and%20posters%20of%20the%20Ram%20temple%20built%20in%20Ayodhya%20have%20been%20put%20up%20by%20the%20BJP%20across%20the%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%20The%20posters%20announce%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3EBhavya%20Ram%20Mandir%20bankar%20ho%20raha%20hai%20taiyyar%2C%20fir%20iss%20baar%20BJP%20Sarkar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(A%20grand%20Ram%20temple%20is%20being%20readied%2C%20this%20time%20again%20there%20will%20be%20a%20BJP%20government).%E2%80%9D%20It%20may%20not%20have%20been%20a%20coincidence%20that%20the%20posters%20suddenly%20sprung%20up%20in%20the%20state%20during%20Amit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20three-day%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20is%20it%20not%20resonating%20with%20people%3F%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20expectation%2C%20its%20desperate%20attempt%20to%20whip%20up%20religious%20fervour%20among%20the%20voters%20in%20the%20poll-bound%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20around%20the%20Ram%20temple%20has%20evoked%20a%20sense%20of%20d%C3%A9j%C3%A0%20vu.%20The%20issue%20is%20not%20resonating%20with%20the%20electorate.%20Nor%20has%20it%20charged%20up%20the%20party%20cadres%2C%20most%20of%20whom%20are%20too%20confused%20and%20dismayed%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-infighting-state-elections%5C%22%3Einfighting%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20tickets%20for%20constituencies%20to%20get%20nostalgic%20about%20the%20three-decade-long%20Ram%20Janambhoomi%20movement%20that%20culminated%20in%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22650%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20.jpg%20650w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F11%2F23120832%2Fl7l9chag_ram-temple-proposed-design-august-2020_625x300_04_August_20-300x185.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-629759%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22400%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EThe%20design%20for%20the%20Ram%20Temple%20in%20Ayodhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20BJP%20leaders%20played%20up%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinsult%E2%80%9D%20to%20Sanatana%20Dharma%20by%20harping%20over%20the%20controversial%20comment%20of%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20leader%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-attacking-udhayanidhi-stalin-over-sanatana-dharma-remarks%5C%22%3EUdhayanidhi%20Stalin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20linking%20it%20to%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20view%20by%20citing%20the%20two%20parties%E2%80%99%20association%20to%20the%20INDIA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAt%20Jan%20Ashirwad%20(public%20blessings)%20rallies%2C%20the%20BJP%20played%20the%20Hindutva%20card%2C%20focusing%20its%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%20over%20the%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20controversy.%20On%20September%2014%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20said%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20trying%20to%20destroy%20Sanatan%20Dharma.%20The%20BJP%20has%20also%20been%20highlighting%20its%20development%20of%20religious%20tourist%20circuits%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Mahakal%20Lok%20corridor%20in%20Ujjain%20and%20the%20Adi%20Shankaracharya%20statue%20in%20Omkareshwar.%20But%20the%20electorates%20don%E2%80%99t%20appear%20impressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmadhya-pradesh-bjp-shivraj-singh-chouhan-centre%5C%22%3EWith%20a%20Split%20House%20for%20the%20BJP%20in%20MP%2C%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%20Is%20Fighting%20for%20Himself%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20apparent%20indifference%20among%20voters%20to%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20to%20galvanise%20them%20around%20the%20tried%20and%20tested%20Hindutva%20pitch%20is%20not%20surprising.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFour%20factors%20behind%20apparent%20apathy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EPolitical%20observers%20attribute%20the%20apathy%20to%20mainly%20four%20factors.%20One%2C%20the%20secular%20issues%20such%20as%20unemployment%2C%20price-rise%20and%20corruption%20are%20too%20overarching%20ones%20in%20this%20election%20to%20be%20subsumed%20by%20communal%20politics.%20The%20Congress%20is%20staying%20focused%20on%20these%20issues%2C%20sensing%20support%20to%20the%20party%20on%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETwo%2C%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20promise%20for%20caste%20census%20has%20revived%20the%20Mandal%20versus%20Kamandal%20narrative%2C%20causing%20Other%20Backward%20Castes%20to%20priotise%20caste%20above%20religion.%20Caste%20has%20emerged%20as%20a%20more%20dominant%20issue%20in%20this%20election.%20Both%20the%20main%20parties%20have%20been%20pretty%20sensitive%20to%20the%20narrative%20and%20allotted%20more%20than%2027%25%20seats%20to%20the%20OBCs%20who%20account%20for%20nearly%2050%25%20of%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Muslims%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20are%20too%20few%20and%20too%20scattered%20for%20majoritarian%20triumphalism%20on%20the%20Ram%20temple%20at%20their%20expense.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFourth%20%E2%80%93%20and%20arguably%20the%20most%20important%20factor%20%E2%80%93%20is%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20astute%2C%20if%20controversial%2C%20strategy%20to%20neutralise%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20Hindutva%20by%20deploying%20the%20rival%E2%80%99s%20religious%20symbolism%20with%20equal%20vigour.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20divert%20people%E2%80%99s%20attention%20away%20from%20anti-incumbency%20sentiments%20against%20the%20state%20government%20is%20proving%20ineffective.%20But%20the%20BJP%20seems%20to%20be%20left%20with%20no%20option%20but%20to%20push%20through%20its%20core%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20its%20ploys%20such%20as%20invisibilising%20chief%20minister%20Shivraj%20Singh%20Chouhan%E2%80%99s%20performance%20in%20the%20last%2018%20years%2C%20sole%20focus%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20achievements%2C%20deployment%20of%20seven%20MPs%20including%20three%20union%20ministers%20and%20centralising%20the%20campaign%20have%20failed%20to%20brighten%20up%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20prospects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20opinion%20polls%20had%20forecast%20Congress%20victory%20over%20the%20BJP%20with%20a%20slim%20margin.%20The%20latest%20opinion%20poll%20conducted%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsdayexpress.com%2Fpolitics%2Fthe-survey-after-rebellion-put-bjp-in-tension-inflation-is-the-biggest-issue-in-the-elections%2F%5C%22%3EZee-C4%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20forecast%20132-146%20seats%20to%20the%20Congress%20and%2084-98%20seats%20to%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMore%20remarkably%2C%20the%20opinion%20poll%20has%20predicted%2046%25%20vote%20share%20to%20the%20Congress%20against%2043%25%20to%20the%20BJP.%20This%20survey%20was%20done%20after%20the%20battle%20lines%20had%20been%20drawn%20and%20candidates%20for%20both%20parties%20had%20been%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20neutralising%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20match%20the%20BJP%20in%20liberally%20flaunting%20religious%20symbolism%20was%20frown%20upon%20by%20a%20section%20in%20the%20Congress%2C%20it%20has%20proved%20effective%20in%20blunting%20the%20opponent%E2%80%99s%20edge%20on%20Hindutva.%20The%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20ministerial%20candidate%20has%20tactfully%20ensured%20that%20the%20BJP%20oft-repeated%20claim%20in%20the%20past%20about%20the%20Congress%20being%20anti-Hindu%20sounded%20incredible%2C%20at%20least%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22800%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n.jpeg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n-200x300.jpeg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151458%2F367384106_900743161408994_2449008609315507060_n-683x1024.jpeg%20683w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-671843%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ECongress%20leader%20Kamal%20Nath.%20Photo%3A%20Facebook%2FKamal%20Nath%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3ENath%20has%20worn%20his%20Hinduness%20on%20his%20sleeve.%20He%20has%20often%20reacted%20to%20the%20charge%20of%20practising%20soft-hindutva%20by%2