etimes%20they%20call%20Lord%20Ram%20imaginary.%20This%20country%20cannot%20run%20without%20Lord%20Ram.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20reaction%2C%20Congress%20stalwart%20Digvijaya%20Singh%20said%20that%20he%20is%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgood%20Hindu%E2%80%9D%20and%20has%20donated%20more%20money%20than%20chief%20minister%20Chouhan%20to%20the%20Ram%20temple.%20But%20the%20use%20of%20religion%20in%20elections%20is%20barred.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20former%20chief%20minister%20Kamal%20Nath%20had%20asked%2C%20%E2%80%9CIs%20Ram%20mandir%20the%20temple%20of%20BJP%3F%20It%20is%20the%20temple%20of%20every%20person%20of%20this%20country.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20replica%20of%20Sanatan%20Dharma%20and%20I%20am%20happy%20that%20Ram%20temple%20is%20being%20constructed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmit%20Shah%E2%80%99s%20three%20Diwali%20claim%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Mandir%20took%20centre%20stage%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20after%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%20said%20that%20the%20state%20is%20set%20to%20celebrate%20Diwali%20festival%20thrice%20in%20the%20coming%20months%20%E2%80%94%20on%20the%20day%20of%20Diwali%2C%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20state%20poll%20results%2C%20and%20when%20the%20temple%20is%20inaugurated%20in%20Ayodhya%20in%20January%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20230-member%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20is%20set%20to%20go%20to%20polls%20on%20November%2017%2C%20with%20the%20vote%20count%20taking%20place%20on%20December%203%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698665444000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F09%2F07151156%2F374943054_878995983596801_1036847113504325148_n.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-bjps-hindutva-campaign-is-not-working-in-madhya-pradesh%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Although%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Congress%20chief%20Kamal%20Nath%E2%80%99s%20strategy%20to%20match%20the%20BJP%20in%20liberally%20flaunting%20reli