he%20poor%2C%20in%20their%20command%20areas%20through%20unnecessary%20inconvenience.%20This%20consolidation%20was%20neither%20demanded%20by%20the%20customers%20nor%20by%20the%20shareholders%2C%20nor%20by%20the%20employees.%20As%20was%20being%20argued%20by%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FOpinion%2FD2mfHcAdkiZPeOthBjnL3N%2FThe-whys-and-hows-of-bank-consolidation-in-India.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egovernment%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20some%20academicians%2C%20this%20was%20proposed%20to%20help%20reduce%20administrative%20costs%2C%20increase%20risk%20appetite%2C%20provide%20better%20capitalisation%20etc.%20But%20the%20same%20now%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20an%20alibi.%20Rather%2C%20bank%20consolidation%20and%20the%20formation%20of%20bigger%20entities%20help%20corporate%20borrowers%20raise%20finances%20from%20a%20single%20financial%20institution.%20Banks%20have%20to%20adhere%20to%20RBI%E2%80%99s%20stipulated%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Frbi-hikes-group-expousre-limit-of-banks-to-30-till-30-june-2020-11590124601551.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Egroup-specific%20exposure%20limit%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20refers%20to%20the%20maximum%20loan%20as%20a%20percentage%20of%20its%20capital%20base%20that%20a%20bank%20can%20offer%20to%20a%20specific%20business%20client.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Since%20mergers%20increase%20the%20capital%20base%20of%20the%20new%20entity%2C%20they%20allow%20corporate%20lenders%20to%20seek%20loans%20from%20a%20lesser%20number%20of%20banks%20rather%20than%20approach%20many%20financial%20institutions%20to%20raise%20money.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConsolidation%20of%20PSBs%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20boon%20for%20private%20banks.%20During%20the%20period%202017%20to%202022%2C%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fmoney-and-banking%2Fpublic-sector-banks-psbs-private-sector-banks-pvsbs-employee-count-branches-business-per-employee-consolidation-amalgamation-rationalisation-average-business-per-employee-v-viswanathan-s-nagarajan-all%2Farticle67366088.ece%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Enumber%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20branches%20of%20PSBs%20has%20gone%20down%20from%2091%2C445%20to%2084%2C256%20while%20that%20of%20private%20sector%20banks%20has%20gone%20up%20from%2024%2C661%20to%2037%2C872.%20This%20excludes%20the%2012%20small%20finance%20banks%20and%20six%20payment%20banks%20which%20have%20added%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fhrdc.gujaratuniversity.ac.in%2FUploads%2FEJournalDetail%2F30%2F1046%2F74.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ethousands%20of%20branches%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%202016-17%20to%202020-21.%20This%20had%20an%20obvious%20effect%20on%20business.%20As%20against%202019%2C%20in%202023%20business%20of%20public%20sector%20banks%20has%20grown%20by%2038.35%25%20while%20in%20the%20case%20of%20private%20sector%20banks%2C%20this%20growth%20is%20by%2067.30%25%2C%20as%20per%20data%20collated%20by%20the%20author.%20This%20data%20speaks%20for%20itself.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20space%20which%20public%20sector%20banks%20have%20vacated%20consequent%20upon%20consolidation%20has%20been%20occupied%20by%20private%20sector%20banks%20and%20thus%20it%20shows%20that%20even%20though%20banks%20have%20not%20been%20privatised%2C%20banking%20business%20is%20being%20privatised%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20the%20main%20agenda%20of%20Indian%20corporates%20as%20also%20of%20international%20finance%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EThe%20non-solutions%20of%20the%20IBC%20regime%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20government%20has%20been%20claiming%20that%20the%20Insolvency%20and%20Bankruptcy%20Code%20(IBC)%2C%202016%20has%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20game%20changer.%20Since%20its%20establishment%2C%20only%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F47-of-insolvency-cases-resolved-via-liquidation-details-here-11650042866335.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E14%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20NPA%20accounts%20referred%20to%20the%20IBC%20were%20resolved%20through%20resolution%20plans.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20recovery%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2F47-of-insolvency-cases-resolved-via-liquidation-details-here-11650042866335.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E31%25%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20the%20amount%20which%20was%20due%20but%20only%20with%20the%20sacrifice%20of%2069%25.%20The%20IBC%20has%20clearly%20not%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20promised%20panacea%20for%20the%20NPAs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENor%20has%20the%20IBC%20had%20a%20deterrent%20effect%20on%20defaulters.%20According%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsuit.cibil.com%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edata%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20collated%20by%20Transunion%20Cibil%2C%20a%20credit%20information%20company%2C%20there%20was%20a%20notable%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20wilful%20defaulter%20accounts%20at%20all%20%E2%80%98credit%20institutions%E2%80%99%20between%20March%202018%20and%20March%202022.%20During%20this%20period%2C%20the%20count%20of%20such%20accounts%20rose%20from%2020%2C066%20to%2031%2C026%2C%20for%20loan%20defaults%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20and%20above.%20This%20signifies%20a%2064.67%25%20uptick%20in%20the%20number%20of%20accounts.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndividuals%20involved%20in%20illicit%20activities%20within%20the%20corporate%20sector%2C%20particularly%20those%20seeking%20to%20defraud%20financial%20institutions%2C%20appear%20to%20be%20displaying%20increased%20enthusiasm%20for%20their%20wrongful%20actions.%20Their%20growing%20confidence%20likely%20arises%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20they%20can%20escape%20legal%20repercussions.%20A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cenfa.org%2Frbi-supports-frauds-and-wilful-defaulters-why%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eperception%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20seems%20to%20find%20support%20in%20the%20contentious%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbi.org.in%2FScripts%2FNotificationUser.aspx%3FId%3D12513%26Mode%3D0%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecircular%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20issued%20by%20the%20RBI%20on%20June%208%2C%202023%2C%20that%20spoke%20of%20a%20framework%20for%20compromise%20settlements%20and%20write-offs%20for%20wilful%20defaulters%20and%20fraudsters.%20The%20RBI%20was%20forced%20to%20issue%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rbi.org.in%2Fcommonperson%2FEnglish%2FScripts%2FFAQs.aspx%3FId%3D3459%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eclarification%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3Eexplaining%20that%20it%20had%20a%20stand%20on%20settlements%20with%20wilful%20defaulters%20and%20fraudsters%20for%2015%20years!%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20lenient%20approach%20adopted%20by%20both%20the%20government%20and%20the%20RBI%20carries%20significant%20implications%20for%20evaluating%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20the%20IBC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20past%20decade%20stands%20witness%20to%20hollow%20claims%20by%20the%20government%20of%20having%20tackled%20the%20menace%20of%20non-performing%20assets.%20Rather%2C%20the%20government%20has%20bailed%20out%20the%20corporations%20through%20rising%20haircuts%2C%20remission%20and%20write-offs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EDevidas%20Tuljapurkar%20is%20the%20joint%20secretary%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Bank%20Employees%20Association%20and%20a%20former%20director%20of%20the%20Bank%20of%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698662125000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F19143244%2FF1THyNVWcAAkEk1.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fa-decade-of-write-offs-how-the-govt-and-banks-failed-to-tackle-npas-and-helped-big-corporations%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20has%20time%20and%20again%20stated%20that%20%E2%80%98write%20off%E2%80%99%20does%20not%20mean%20relief%20to%20the%20borrower%20as%20recovery%20processes%20continue.%20But%20in%20practice%2C%20banks%20are%20compelled%20to%20forgo%20any%20hope%20of%20recovery.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A35%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbanking%2Fa-decade-of-write-offs-how-the-govt-and-banks-failed-to-tackle-npas-and-helped-big-corporations%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indians%E2%80%99%20Personal%20Data%20Breached%20Yet%20Again%2C%20but%20No%20Sign%20That%20Gaps%20Will%20Be%20Plugged%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30142939%2Fcyber-security-1923446_1280.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIndia%20is%20rapidly%20digitising.%20There%20are%20good%20things%20and%20bad%2C%20speed-bumps%20on%20the%20way%20and%20caveats%20to%20be%20mindful%20of.%20The%20weekly%20column%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerminal%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0focuses%20on%20all%20that%20is%20connected%20and%20is%20not%20%E2%80%93%20on%20digital%20issues%2C%20policy%2C%20ideas%20and%20themes%20dominating%20the%20conversation%20in%20India%20and%20the%20world.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResecurity%2C%20a%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20US%20cybersecurity%20firm%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0published%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.resecurity.com%2Fblog%2Farticle%2Fpii-belonging-to-indian-citizens-including-their-aadhaar-ids-offered-for-sale-on-the-dark-web%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eblog%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cspan%3Eearly%20October%20pointing%20towards%20a%20general%20trend%20of%20the%20personal%20data%20of%20Indians%20being%20sold%20over%20the%20dark%20web.%20The%20firm%20found%20that%20a%20threat%20actor%20had%20advertised%20the%20sale%20of%20close%20to%20815%20million%20Aadhaar%20records%20for%20%2480%2C000.%20The%20blog%2C%20citing%20other%20instances%20when%20Indians%E2%80%99%20personal%20information%20was%20put%20up%20for%20sale%2C%20raised%20concerns%20about%20identity%20theft.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20threat%20actor%20with%20the%20alias%20%E2%80%98pwn0001%E2%80%99%20claimed%20that%20they%20could%20sell%20records%20of%20815%20million%20Indians%2C%20including%20names%2C%20ages%2C%20phone%20numbers%2C%20Aadhaar%20numbers%20and%20addresses.%20pwn0001%20shared%20a%20sample%2C%20which%20had%201%20lakh%20phone%20numbers%20and%20Aadhaar%20numbers.%20The%20sample%20dataset%20includes%20personal%20information%20of%20children%20as%20young%20as%2010.%20It%20is%20yet%20unclear%20from%20which%20database%20the%20records%20of%2081.5%20crore%20Indians%2C%20including%20children%E2%80%99s%20Personally%20Identifiable%20Information%20(PII)%2C%20have%20been%20breached.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.news18.com%2Findia%2Findias-biggest-data-leak-so-far-covid-19-test-info-of-81-5cr-citizens-with-icmr-up-for-sale-exclusive-8637743.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ENews18%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20report%20claims%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%E2%80%99s%20database%20was%20breached.%20The%20report%20also%20claims%20Indian%20Computer%20Emergency%20Response%20Team%20(CERT-In)%20has%20informed%20ICMR%20of%20the%20breach%20and%20it%20has%20to%20verify%20it.%20If%20this%20indeed%20proves%20to%20be%20the%20case%2C%20it%20is%20unclear%20why%20ICMR%20would%20have%20details%20of%2010-year-olds.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20push%20to%20link%20Aadhaar%20cards%20to%20everything%20has%20proliferated%20the%20personal%20data%20of%20Indians%20across%20cyberspace%2C%20among%20various%20public%20and%20private%20firms.%20There%20are%20a%20few%20databases%20with%20such%20large-scale%20personal%20data%20of%20Indians%2C%20but%20it%20is%20uncertain%20which%20database%20would%20have%20been%20breached.%20While%20the%20sample%20dataset%20can%20help%20us%20verify%20the%20genuineness%20of%20the%20data%20that%20has%20been%20put%20up%20for%20sale%2C%20it%20would%20still%20be%20hard%20to%20verify%20the%20source.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResecurity%20points%20to%20another%20threat%20actor%20with%20the%20alias%20%E2%80%9CLucius%E2%80%9D%2C%20who%20has%20put%20up%20Indian%20law%20enforcement%20data%20for%20sale.%20According%20to%20Lucius%2C%2085%25%20of%20Indians%E2%80%99%20personal%20data%20%E2%80%93%20including%20phone%20numbers%2C%20identity%20documents%20and%20addresses%20%E2%80%93%20are%20available%20in%20this%20dataset%20for%20sale.%20The%20sample%20dataset%20shared%20by%20Lucius%20indicates%20KYC%20data%20of%20mobile%20connections%20with%20columns%20for%20prepaid%20and%20postpaid%20being%20available%20in%20the%20dataset.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResecurity%E2%80%99s%20analysis%20shows%20that%20as%20data%20sharing%20is%20forced%20on%20Indians%2C%20more%20threat%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3Eactors%20will%20be%20able%20to%20access%20large-scale%20PII%20data.%20This%20is%20not%20a%20new%20trend%20for%20many%20Indians%2C%20who%20have%20been%20used%20to%20hearing%20news%20of%20Aadhaar%20data%20breaches.%20What%20is%20evident%2C%20though%2C%20is%20that%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20breach%20and%20the%20size%20of%20the%20data%20are%20growing.%20This%20trend%20too%20can%20be%20attributed%20to%20the%20proliferation%20of%20Aadhaar%20across%20India%E2%80%99s%20data%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20US%20cybersecurity%20firm%20is%20primarily%20concerned%20with%20the%20associated%20identity%20fraud%20that%20will%20follow%20these%20large-scale%20data%20breaches%20%E2%80%93%20online%20banking%20fraud%2C%20tax%20refund%20fraud%20and%20other%20financial%20crimes.%20Aadhaar-based%20frauds%20have%20become%20quite%20common%20in%20India%20and%20yet%2C%20the%20regulator%20won%E2%80%99t%20address%20the%20problem%20at%20hand.%20UIDAI%20has%20virtually%20ignored%20the%20Aadhaar%20data%20leaks%2C%20while%20promising%20us%20a%20virtual%20ID%20solution%20that%20disappeared%20after%20the%20litigation%20around%20Aadhaar%20concluded%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIdentifying%20the%20breach%20and%20plugging%20it%20would%20be%20important%20to%20critically%20address%20the%20issue%20of%20cybersecurity%20and%20safety%20for%20Indians.%20October%20is%20celebrated%20as%20%E2%80%9CCyberSecurity%20Awareness%20Month%E2%80%9D%20by%20CERT-In.%20Yet%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20really%20get%20much%20cybersecurity%20awareness%20other%20than%20basic%20tips%20and%20tricks.%20The%20cybersecurity%20landscape%20is%20fast%20changing%20with%20increasing%20data%20breaches%20and%20we%20need%20CERT-In%20to%20provide%20actual%20solutions%20instead%20of%20following%20a%20%E2%80%9Csecurity-through-obscurity%E2%80%9D%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20panic%20or%20hysteria%20surrounding%20this%20breach.%20The%20inaction%20and%20continuous%20forcing%20of%20Aadhaar%20against%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20orders%20are%20concerning.%20Indians%20deserve%20better%20cybersecurity%20than%20what%20is%20currently%20in%20place.%20The%20implementation%20of%20the%20Digital%20Personal%20Data%20Protection%20Act%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Cspan%3E2023%20can%20address%20some%20of%20these%20issues%20but%20as%20long%20as%20government%20exemptions%20remain%2C%20data%20for%20government%20networks%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20breached.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20true%20safety%2C%20Indians%20need%20to%20be%20provided%20with%20privacy.%20Instead%2C%20we%20are%20only%20offered%20security%20in%20terms%20of%20data%20protection.%20Even%20this%20promise%20of%20data%20protection%20is%20faulty%2C%20with%20no%20actual%20resources%20being%20allocated%20towards%20cybersecurity%20operations.%20India%E2%80%99s%20current%20paradigm%20of%20security%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20address%20the%20emerging%20challenges%20people%20are%20facing.%20UIDAI%2C%20the%20RBI%2C%20CERT-In%20and%20the%20information%20technology%20ministry%20should%20all%20at%20least%20acknowledge%20what%20is%20at%20stake%20when%20they%20force%20Aadhaar%20on%20Indians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fskodali%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ESrinivas%20Kodali%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20a%20researcher%20on%20digitisation%20and%20a%20hacktivist.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698661837000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30142939%2Fcyber-security-1923446_1280.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findians-personal-data-breached-yet-again-but-no-sign-that-gaps-will-be-plugged%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20US%20cybersecurity%20firm%20found%20that%20a%20threat%20actor%20had%20advertised%20the%20sale%20of%20close%20to%20815%20million%20Aadhaar%20records%20for%20a%20price%20of%20%2480%2C000.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Ftech%2Findians-personal-data-breached-yet-again-but-no-sign-that-gaps-will-be-plugged%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lucknow%3A%20Former%20BJP%20MP's%20Son%20Dies%20Allegedly%20Due%20to%20Lack%20of%20Beds%20in%20Hospital%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30154944%2F49007467_105369040525953_6926840452314300416_n.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAfter%20his%20son%20passed%20away%20at%20Lucknow%E2%80%99s%20Sanjay%20Gandhi%20Postgraduate%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20(SGPGI)%2C%20former%20Banda%20MP%20Bhairon%20Prasad%20Mishra%20sat%20on%20dharna%20at%20the%20hospital%20o