of%20the%20chants%20that%20echoed%20through%20Grand%20Central%20Station%20was%2C%20%E2%80%9CNever%20again%20for%20anyone%2C%20never%20again%20is%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%20This%2C%20for%20us%2C%20is%20the%20most%20basic%20lesson%20of%20the%20Holocaust%20that%20many%20Jews%20seem%20to%20have%20forgotten.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20pain%20as%20a%20Hindu%20has%20been%20that%20Hinduism%20has%20been%20hijacked%20by%20Hindu%20supremacists%2C%20led%20by%20the%20likes%20of%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20Adityanath.%20They%20are%20entrenching%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20India%20and%20abroad%20with%20a%20false%20sense%20of%20victimhood%20and%20danger%20from%20our%20Muslim%20siblings%2C%20and%20increasing%20Islamophobic%20sentiment.%20Under%20the%20current%20regime%2C%20India%20is%20being%20transformed%20into%20a%20Hindu%20%3Cem%3Erashtra%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E(nation)%20where%20Muslims%20and%20other%20religious%20minorities%20are%20neither%20welcome%20nor%20safe.%20Protesting%20with%20thousands%20of%20Jews%20calling%20for%20a%20ceasefire%20in%20Gaza%20made%20me%20dream%20of%20a%20day%20when%20thousands%20%E2%80%93%20or%20even%20hundreds%20%E2%80%93%20of%20Hindus%20will%20gather%20to%20say%20%E2%80%98not%20in%20my%20name%E2%80%99%20to%20violence%20committed%20by%20Hindu%20supremacists.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThroughout%20the%20protest%2C%20I%20held%20India%20in%20my%20heart.%20I%20am%20dismayed%20that%20India%2C%20a%20country%20which%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Fnews-ians%2Findia-hailed-for-giving-refuge-to-jews-fleeing-nazi-genocide-119012900174_1.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ealways%20a%20refuge%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20against%20anti-semitism%20for%20the%20Jewish%20people%2C%20while%20also%20being%20(at%20least%20in%20rhetoric)%20pro-Palestine%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20West%20Asian%20conflict%2C%20has%20shifted%20so%20drastically%20under%20Modi.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20its%20own%20partition%20bloodbath%2C%20India%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fdefence%2Fhow-india-went-from-voting-against-israel-creation-to-a-close-defence-partner%2F1803452%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eneither%20voted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20partition%20of%20Palestine%20in%201947%20to%20create%20the%20nation%20of%20Israel%2C%20nor%20for%20Israel%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20in%201949.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Findia-refuses-to-back-landslide-un-general-assembly-call-for-humanitarian-truce-in-gaza%5C%22%3EIndia%20Refuses%20to%20Back%20Landslide%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20Call%20for%20Humanitarian%20Truce%20in%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAzad%20Essa%20details%20in%20his%20book%20%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHostile%20Homelands%3A%20The%20New%20Alliance%20Between%20Israel%20and%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20how%20this%20shift%20towards%20being%20an%20ally%20of%20Israel%20occurred%20gradually%20since%20even%20before%20Indian%20independence%2C%20but%20has%20become%20much%20more%20extreme%20during%20the%20Modi%20regime.%C2%A0%20Though%20the%20Indian%20population%20remains%20largely%20sympathetic%20to%20the%20Palestinian%20fight%20for%20self-determination%2C%20the%20diplomatic%20relationship%20has%20been%20reshaped%20by%20the%20weapons%20trade%20and%20ideology.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20now%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F10%2F11%2Fhow-big-is-israels-military-and-how-much-funding-does-it-get-from-the-us%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elargest%20purchaser%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20of%20Israeli%20weapons%20and%20military%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20reach%20130%20billion%20dollars%20over%20the%20next%20five%20years.%C2%A0%20Further%2C%20Hindutva%20