leased%20in%20late%20July%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fjuly-2023-the-hottest-ever-month-on-record-likely-warmest-in-tens-of-thousands-of-years%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esaid%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20it%20was%20the%20hottest%20month%20the%20world%20has%20seen%20since%20records%20began%3B%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20reports%2C%20it%20could%20be%20the%20hottest%20in%20%E2%80%9Ctens%20of%20thousands%20of%20years%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAmong%20the%20recent%20climate-related%20extremes%20mentioned%20in%20the%20paper%20that%20Huq%20co-authored%20are%20the%20heavy%20monsoonal%20rains%20that%20caused%20flash%20floods%20and%20landslides%20in%20northern%20India%20that%20killed%20more%20than%20100%20people%20in%20July%202023.%20%E2%80%9CClimate%20change%20is%20likely%20making%20monsoons%20in%20this%20region%20more%20variable%2C%20causing%20frequent%20landslides%20and%20floods%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20authors%20wrote%20in%20the%20paper.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20paper%20serves%20as%20a%20scary%20warning.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20scientists%2C%20we%20are%20increasingly%20being%20asked%20to%20tell%20the%20public%20the%20truth%20about%20the%20crises%20we%20face%20in%20simple%20and%20direct%20terms%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20authors%2C%20including%20Huq%2C%20wrote.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20truth%20is%20that%20we%20are%20shocked%20by%20the%20ferocity%20of%20the%20extreme%20weather%20events%20in%202023.%20We%20are%20afraid%20of%20the%20uncharted%20territory%20that%20we%20have%20now%20entered.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20September%2024%20this%20year%2C%2015%2C484%20scientists%20are%20signatory%20to%20the%20warning.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EHuge%20loss%20for%20Global%20South%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENumerous%20climate%20experts%20and%20officials%20have%20expressed%20shock%20at%20his%20death%2C%20and%20for%20the%20loss%20this%20means%20to%20the%20climate%20science%20discourse%2C%20especially%20for%20the%20Global%20South.%20Huq%20was%20among%20the%20many%20climate%20experts%20who%20had%20been%20instrumental%20in%20the%20setting%20up%20of%20the%20historic%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20fund%20at%20the%20last%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20at%20Glasgow%2C%20Scotland%20(COP27).%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fnews-and-stories%2Fstory%2Fwhat-you-need-know-about-cop27-loss-and-damage-fund%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EUN%20Evironment%20Programme%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20loss%20and%20damage%20%E2%80%9Crefers%20to%20the%20negative%20consequences%20that%20arise%20from%20the%20unavoidable%20risks%20of%20climate%20change%E2%80%9D%2C%20from%20rising%20sea%20levels%20to%20extreme%20weather%20events%20such%20as%20heatwaves%20and%20intense%20bouts%20of%20rainfall.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeveloping%20countries%2C%20including%20Bangladesh%20and%20India%2C%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20climate%20change%20due%20to%20the%20increasing%20intensity%20of%20such%20events%20made%20more%20likely%20by%20climate%20change.%20The%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund%20aims%20to%20finance%20climate%20change%20mitigation%20and%20adaptation%20in%20developing%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20an%20emotional%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fharjeet11%2Fstatus%2F1718621283376640272%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Harjeet%20Singh%2C%20head%20of%20global%20political%20strategy%20with%20Climate%20Action%20Network%20International%20said%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Chard%20to%20grasp%E2%80%9D%20that%20Huq%20won%E2%80%99t%20be%20at%20COP28%2C%20especially%20when%20he%20had%20attended%20all%2027%20preceding%20COPs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CTogether%2C%20we%20fought%20for%20the%20establishment%20of%20the%20Loss%20and%20Damage%20Fund.%20The%20battle%20for%20climate%20justice%20remains%20ongoing%E2%80%A6I%20pledge%20to%20redouble%20my%20efforts%2C%20to%20uphold%20the%20torch%2C%20and%20to%20champion%20the%20cause%20with%20even%20more%20passion%20and%20hard%20work.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20do%20this%20in%20honour%20of%20your%20legacy%2C%20feeling%20your%20guidance%20and%20blessings%20from%20the%20heavens%20above%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fharjeet11%2Fstatus%2F1718621283376640272%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweet%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20read.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHuq%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cpioneering%20global%20voice%20on%20adaptation%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20his%20%E2%80%9Cunwavering%20advocacy%20for%20loss%20and%20damage%20finance%E2%80%9D%2C%20were%20%E2%80%9Cjust%20a%20few%20of%20the%20many%20accomplishments%20that%20will%20forever%20be%20etched%20in%20our%20memories%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CA%20huge%20loss%20to%20the%20Climate%20community%20and%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Faditimukherji%2Fstatus%2F1718629891954840036%3Fs%3D20%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Etweeted%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Aditi%20Mukherji%2C%20Director%2C%20Climate%20Change%20Impact%20Platform%20(CGIAR).%20%E2%80%9CMay%20he%20rest%20in%20peace%2C%20and%20May%20everyone%20else%20follow%20his%20legacy%20and%20make%20loss%20and%20damage%20funds%20a%20reality.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20am%20so%20deeply%20saddened%20and%20shocked.%20Saleem%20has%20been%20a%20driving%20force%20for%20climate%20justice%20since%20the%20beginning%20of%20the%20climate%20debate.%20His%20brilliant%20mind%2C%20ability%20to%20say%20what%20has%20to%20be%20said%20and%20dogged%20determination%20have%20been%20beacons%20for%20decades.%20I%20will%20miss%20him%20terribly%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fc