0city%20every%20morning%20to%20sketch%20the%20locomotives.%20I%20would%20spend%20almost%20five%20to%20six%20hours%20every%20day%20doing%20this.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBreathing%20life%20into%20these%20sketches%20through%20watercolour%2C%20oil%2C%20pen%20and%20ink%20was%20a%20fulfilling%20process%20for%20Kishore.%20But%20the%20excitement%20came%20to%20an%20end%20one%20day%20in%201993%20when%20Kishore%20watched%20the%20steam%20locos%20being%20dismantled.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20were%20being%20scrapped%20as%20they%20were%20no%20longer%20being%20operational.%20It%20was%20a%20very%20shocking%20experience%20for%20me%20and%20I%20was%20left%20in%20tears%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%20While%20Kishore%20returned%20to%20Mumbai%20to%20complete%20the%20series%20%E2%80%94%20this%20time%20from%20the%20memory%20of%20what%20he%20had%20seen%20%E2%80%94%20he%20decided%20to%20turn%20it%20into%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F279321%2Fart-beautify-railway-station-project-nilesh-nagra-indore-stunning-pictures%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%20just%20a%20painting%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20the%20engines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20have%20captured%20the%20movement%20of%20people%20including%20the%20fireman%2C%20signalman%2C%20technical%20man%2C%20motorman%20and%20others%20working%20in%20the%20locomotive%20workshops.%20My%20paintings%20always%20have%20a%20deep%20expression%20of%20the%20characters%2C%20with%20dark%2C%20bearded%20faces%20sporting%20a%20red%20%3Cem%3Epagdi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(turban)%20which%20looks%20very%20unusual%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20a%20chance%20for%20you%20to%20travel%20through%20time%20through%20these%20artworks%20by%20Kishore%3A%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20800px)%20100vw%2C%20800px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-me