2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientist%2FEngineer%20(SC)%20(Electrical%20engineering%2Felectrical%20and%20electronics%20engineering)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20be%20between%2018%20and%2028%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20should%20have%20a%20BE%2FBTech%20or%20equivalent%20qualification%20in%20the%20discipline%20with%20a%20minimum%20aggregate%20of%2065%20percent%20marks%20or%20a%20CGPA%2FCPI%20grading%20of%206.84%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScientist%2FEngineer%20(SC)%20(MSc%20agriculture%20%5Bhorticulture%2Fforestry%5D)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThe%20candidate%20should%20be%20between%2018%20and%2028%20years%20of%20age.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3ECandidates%20must%20hold%20an%20MSc%20or%20an%20equivalent%20postgraduate%20degree%20in%20the%20field%20with%20a%20minimum%20aggregate%20of%2065%20percent%20marks%20or%20a%20CGPA%2FCPI%20grading%20of%206.84%20on%20a%2010-point%20scale.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3C%2Fol%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThings%20to%20know%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Col%3E%20%3Cli%3EThere%20will%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310225%2Ftech-tools-to-use-for-competitive-exam-preparation-iit-upsc-ias-officer-divya-mittal%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewritten%20test%20for%20candidates%3C%2Fa%3E%20based%20on%20their%20curriculum%20through%20offline%20mode%20in%20these%20cities%20%E2%80%94%20Guntur%2C%20Chennai%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20Thiruvananthapuram.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EShortlisted%20candidates%20will%20then%20be%20called%20for%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EAll%20selected%20candidates%20will%20receive%20a%20salary%20of%20Rs%2079%2C662%20per%20month%20along%20with%20HRA%20and%20transport%20allowance.%3C%2Fli%3E%20%3Cli%3EUpon%20appointment%2C%20selected%20candidates%20will%20be%20under%20the%20purview%20of%20the%20National%20P